(1, 62, 'Gii thiu v chng ti', 'gi-i-thi-u', '<h2 class=\"detail-sapo\" data-role=\"sapo\"><em><strong>Sau ba thng xy dng v th nghim, ngy 11/12/2003, trang web ca bo tc l Bo Kin Giang online chnh thc ra mt. Khi nhp chut vo a ch www.baokiengiang.com.vn, khng ch mt t bo vi ni dung phong ph, c sc c cp nht tng gi hin ra m bn c cn c cung cp mt ni dung truyn thng a phng tin c bit hp dn.</strong></em></h2>\r\n<h3>Gii Thiu</h3>\r\n<p>Vi s pht trin khng ngng ca cng ngh thng tin, vic tip cn thng tin nhanh chng v hiu qu  tr thnh mt yu t quan trng trong cuc sng hng ngy ca chng ta. Trong tnh hnh ny, Trang web <strong>Bo Kin Giang</strong>  ni ln nh mt ngun thng tin ng tin cy, a dng v y , p ng nhu cu cn thit ca cng ng trc tuyn.</p>\r\n<h3>a Dng Thng Tin</h3>\r\n<p><strong>Bo Kin Giang</strong> khng ch cung cp tin tc nng hi v cc s kin hng ngy m cn mang n i ng phng vin chuyn nghip, nm bt thng tin t mi lnh vc nh chnh tr, kinh t, vn ha, x hi, gio dc, v nhiu lnh vc khc. iu ny gip ngi c c ci nhn ton din v s pht trin ca tnh Kin Giang v c nc.</p>\r\n<h3>Tin Tc Nhanh Chng v Cp Nht</h3>\r\n<p>Vi tc  pht trin ca th gii ngy nay, thng tin nhanh chng l cha kha quan trng  m bo mi ngi lun cp nht vi nhng s kin mi nht. Bo Kin Giang cam kt cung cp tin tc cp nht 24/7, gip ngi c khng b l bt k thng tin quan trng no.</p>\r\n<h3>Giao Din Thn Thin v D S Dng</h3>\r\n<p>Trang web<strong> Bo Kin Giang</strong> thit k giao din thn thin, d s dng cho mi i tng ngi c. Bn c th d dng tm kim thng tin, c bi vit, v chia s thng tin quan trng vi bn b mt cch thun tin.</p>\r\n<h3>Tng Tc Cng ng</h3>\r\n<p><strong>Bo Kin Giang</strong> khng ch l ni cung cp tin tc m cn l mt nn tng tng tc cng ng mnh m. Ngi c c th tham gia vo cc bnh lun, chia s  kin, v thm ch ng gp thng tin t ngun tin c nhn ca h, to nn mt cng ng trc tuyn a dng v phong ph.</p>\r\n<h3>Su Rng Ch </h3>\r\n<p><strong>Bo Kin Giang</strong> khng ch gii thiu tin tc v cc s kin ln, m cn m phn su rng v cc ch  quan trng ang nh hng n cng ng v x hi. T nhng bi phn tch sc bn, cc bi vit c o v vn ha a phng, n cc bi iu tra cht lng, Bo Kin Giang mang n ci nhn a chiu v phong ph v cuc sng hng ngy.</p>\r\n<h3>c Sn Phong Ph</h3>\r\n<p>Ngoi thng tin chnh, B<strong>o Kin Giang</strong> cn t chc cc c san vi ni dung a dng, c bit v hp dn. Nhng c san ny khng ch l ngun gii tr m cn l cch tuyt vi  c gi hiu r hn v vn ha, lch s, v nhng c im c o ca Kin Giang.</p>\r\n<h3>Tin Tc Video v Multimedia</h3>\r\n<p><strong>Bo Kin Giang</strong> khng ch gii hn  vic cung cp tin tc vn bn, m cn kt hp vi xu hng multimedia hin i. Ngi c c th tri nghim tin tc thng qua video, podcast, v hnh nh sng ng, gip h hiu su hn v s kin v cu chuyn c bo co.</p>\r\n<h3>Chia S  Kin v n nh</h3>\r\n<p><strong>Bo Kin Giang</strong> khng ch dng li  vic cung cp thng tin m cn khuyn khch ngi c th hin  kin ca mnh. Bng cch tham gia vo cc cuc tho lun, thm d  kin, v thm ch gi bi vit c gi, mi ngi c c hi th hin quan im v ng gp vo s pht trin ca cng ng thng tin trc tuyn.</p>\r\n<h3>Cam Kt Cht Lng v  Tin Cy</h3>\r\n<p><strong>Bo Kin Giang</strong> t cht lng v  tin cy ln hng u. Mi thng tin c kim chng k lng trc khi a ln trang web, gip ngi c yn tm v tnh chnh xc v ng tin cy ca thng tin m h nhn c.</p>\r\n<h3>Kt Ni X Hi</h3>\r\n<p><strong>Bo Kin Giang</strong> khng ch tn ti trn trang web m cn kt ni mnh m trn cc nn tng x hi. Ngi c c th theo di, chia s, v tng tc vi Bo Kin Giang qua cc mng x hi ph bin, to nn mt cng ng trc tuyn y  v pht trin.</p>\r\n<h3>Kt Lun</h3>\r\n<p>Trang web <strong>Bo Kin Giang</strong> l ngun thng tin ng tin cy v a dng, em n cho ngi c mt tri nghim tt nht khi khm ph th gii thng tin trn Internet. Hy truy cp ngay  khng b l bt k s kin quan trng no trong v ngoi tnh Kin Giang!</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<div class=\"detail-cmain\"></div>', '', 1, 2, '2024-01-05 00:32:37', 674, '', '2024-01-06 14:34:43', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 00:32:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"flo