(2, 70, 'Kin Giang thiu ct san lp ti cc cng trnh giao thng trng im.', 'kien-giang-thi-u-cat-san-l-p-t-i-cac-cong-trinh-giao-thong-tr-ng-di-m', '<div class=\"article-image\">\r\n<p><img src=\"images/1mvhuynh-6223.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/images/2023/12/26/180126kgo_20231226_7%20le%20viet%20bac.webp\" alt=\"180126kgo_20231226_7 le viet bac\" width=\"717\" height=\"472\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n', '\r\n<h2 class=\"title-italic\">(KGO) - Gim c S Giao thng Vn ti tnh Kin Giang L Vit Bc cho bit Kin Giang s kho st, nh gi tr lng, s ph hp quy chun i vi ct, si ti cc lung ra vo cng, cc ca sng  tn dng khi no vt lung, phc v cho vic san lp mt bng cc cng trnh giao thng, nht l cc cng trnh giao thng ven bin.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"newscontent\">\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid\"><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/images/2023/12/26/180126kgo_20231226_7%20le%20viet%20bac.webp\" alt=\"180126kgo_20231226_7 le viet bac\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid\">Tr li cht vn ca i biu HND tnh ti K hp th hai mi, Gim c S Giao thng Vn ti tnh Kin Giang L Vit Bc cho rng, tnh trng thiu ct san lp trn a bn tnh din ra trm trng, gi c tng cao, nh hng n tin  cc d n giao thng.</div>\r\n<p>Theo Gim c S Giao thng Vn ti tnh Kin Giang L Vit Bc, khan him vt liu ct (sng) san lp mt bng trong xy dng cng trnh l kh khn chung ti khu vc ng bng sng Cu Long. Ti Kin Giang, nhu cu ct (sng) san lp mt bng cc cng trnh xy dng khong 1,7 triu m3, tp trung  cc d n trng im v giao thng. Tuy nhin, ngun cung ct ph thuc hon ton vo cc tnh ln cn nh An Giang, ng Thp, Cn Th v Vnh Long.</p>\r\n<p>Thi gian qua, S Giao thng Vn ti tnh Kin Giang phi hp vi cc n v thi cng trc tip lm vic vi cc doanh nghip cung ng ti An Giang, ng Thp v c h tr ngun cung, bnh qun khong 2.000 m3/ngy.</p>\r\n<p> tho g kh khn ny, S Giao thng Vn ti tnh Kin Giang tham mu UBND tnh Kin Giang tip tc phi hp vi cc n v thi cng tranh th, m phn vi cc oanh nghip cung ng hin ti nng ln khi lng cung ng. ng thi, thc hin a dng ngun cung, thng qua m phn vi cc doanh nghip cung khc, trn a bn khc hoc nhp khu t Campuchia.</p>\r\n<p>Hin nay, B Giao thng Vn ti ang th im thc hin san lp mt bng i vi cng trnh giao thng bng ct bin, d kin cng b kt qu v ban hnh Quy chun k thut trong qu 1-2024.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_1\">\r\n<div id=\"ats-insert_ads-0-wrapper\" class=\"insert_ads insert_ads-2 show_advertisement rendered\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>ADVERTISEMENT</p>\r\n<div id=\"ats-insert_ads-0\" class=\"ats-slot\" data-google-query-id=\"CPKavNjPsYMDFWmC6QUdg0cHGw\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Sau khi Quy chun s dng ct bin trong san lp mt bng i vi cng trnh giao thng c cng b,Kin Giang s kho st nh gi tr lng, tiu chun ph hp cc trn a bn tnh  khai thc, cung ng cho cc cng trnh.</p>\r\n<p>Theo quyt nh ph duyt Quy hoch tnh Kin Giang thi k 2021-2030 tm nhn n 2050, Kin Giang c 18 im c th khai thc ct bin. Tnh s kho st, nh gi tr lng, s ph hp quy chun i vi ct, si ti cc lung ra vo cng, cc ca sng  tn dng khi no vt lung, phc v cho vic san lp mt bng cc cng trnh giao thng, nht l cc cng trnh giao thng ven bin.</p>\r\n<p><strong>TRC LINH</strong></p>\r\n</div>', 1, 8, '2024-01-05 01:02:10', 674, '', '2024-01-06 08:20:56', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:02:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"