iu ti hi ngh.\" width=\"840\" height=\"560\" data-height=\"1365\" data-image-id=\"947744\" data-src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/xpiulqmc/2023_12_25/z5009225727920-71c3e097da55b91d1564e3d8939c4125-1-2903.jpg\" data-width=\"2047\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"caption\">\r\n<p>Gim c S Gio dc v o to tnh Kin Giang, ng Trn Quang Bo pht biu ti hi ngh.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Theo ng Bo, trong qu trnh thc hin, ngnh vn gp mt s kh khn nh: Nhn thc v nng lc, trnh  cng ngh thng tin ca mt s cng chc, vin chc cn hn ch; mt s cng chc, vin chc cha khai thc hiu qu cc cng c phc v chuyn i s; kinh ph mua sm trang thit b cn hn hp. Bn cnh , vic trin khai cng tc chuyn i s  cc trng cha ng b, cha kt ni lin thng ht c s d liu t c s gio dc vi cc c quan qun l phng Gio dc v o to, S Gio dc v o to. Do , nh hng n khai thc, bo co, thng k, d bo ca ngnh.</p>\r\n<p>V mt s nhim v, gii php thc hin chuyn i s ca ngnh, Gim c S Gio dc v o to Kin Giang cho hay: Thi gian ti, Ngnh tip tc tn dng tin b khoa hc cng ngh  thc y i mi sng to trong dy v hc; xy dng nn gio dc m thch ng trn nn tng s. Ch ng c th ha chi tit hn na v phn cng nhim v ca tng cp trong ngnh  thc hin cc hng mc, nhim v cng ngh thng tin v an ton thng tin; xy dng b tiu ch nh gi thc hin chuyn i s trong ngnh; t chc vic nh gi thc hin chuyn i s hng nm ti cc n v.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, Ngnh tng cng bi dng nng cao k nng v cng ngh thng tin cho cn b qun l, gio vin, hc sinh. V u tin tp hun, bi dng qua mng hoc kt hp, tp hun qua mng. Ni dung bi dng gn lin vi nhu cu thc tin v ng dng cng ngh thng tin ca ngnh.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ads_middle\"></div>\r\n<p>Cha dng li  , S Gio dc v o to tnh Kin Giang cn ban hnh hng dn xy dng cc tiu ch, quy nh, quy trnh chuyn mn khi s dng cc phn mm. Thng qua   chuyn cc quy trnh cng vic hin hnh sang thc hin trn mi trng mng, s dng cc h s in t thay cho h s giy ti cc c s gio dc. To c s php l cho nh trng trin khai thun li thc hin chuyn i s v bo m tnh hiu qu.</p>\r\n</div>', 1