n theo di nh gi tr c th nhanh hay chm hn bnh thng hay khng, iu ny rt quan trng trong cc bnh l h hp.</p>\r\n<p>Nu pht hin thy tr c hin tng<a class=\"link-inline-content\" title=\"th kh kh\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.vn/7-nguyen-nhan-gay-tho-kho-khe-thuong-gap-169133999.htm\" data-rel=\"follow\">th kh kh</a>, php phng cnh mi, u gt g theo nhp th, rt lm hm c, rt lm lng ngc, au tai, chy dch tai km theo cc biu hin bt thng khc, th cn a ngay tr ti c s y t  c thm khm v iu tr.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\r\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"Ho c m  tr s cn tr qu trnh h hp. nh minh ho.\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/thuoc-tieu-dom-cho-tre-nen-dung-hay-khong-day-la-cau-tra-loi-cua-chuyen-gia-202104101441548069-17034928944171547814115.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img id=\"img_663660087338524672\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"3 bc x tr ho c m  tr cha m cn bit- nh 2.\" src=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/thuoc-tieu-dom-cho-tre-nen-dung-hay-khong-day-la-cau-tra-loi-cua-chuyen-gia-202104101441548069-17034928944171547814115.jpg\" alt=\"3 bc x tr ho c m  tr cha m cn bit- nh 2.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-adbro-processed=\"true\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/thuoc-tieu-dom-cho-tre-nen-dung-hay-khong-day-la-cau-tra-loi-cua-chuyen-gia-202104101441548069-17034928944171547814115.jpg\" /></a>\r\n<div id=\"adbro\" class=\"adbro-animated adbro-md\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-surf\"></div>\r\n<img src=\"https://bs.serving-sys.com/Serving/adServer.bs?cn=display&amp;c=19&amp;pli=1079857318&amp;gdpr=${GDPR}&amp;gdpr_consent=${GDPR_CONSENT_68}&amp;us_privacy=${US_PRIVACY}&amp;adid=1092111537&amp;ebaddid=ba3964b7d5df43b8bc0bf13d6dfa37a6&amp;ord=1703569208251\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" />\r\n<div id=\"adbro-info-handler\" cl