r, v t di ln  dn lu m t di ln ming, hng. Vng phi ca tr c xc nh t ngang lng tr ln.</p>\r\n<p>Bc v rung c th l: Tay khum li to thnh mt khong trng c khng kh  khi v tr s khng b au (nu  bn tay thng th khi v tr s b au);</p>\r\n<p>Dng lc c tay v rung cho tr, ting v bp bp l ng k thut. Khi v rung ng s cm thy lng ngc ca tr rung ln theo tng nhp v, tr khng h c cm gic au. Lu  khng dng lc cnh tay  v rung, v c th khin tr b au.</p>\r\n<p>V rung trong khong 10 - 15 pht/ln. Sau khi v rung, c th tr s ho nhiu v nn ra m. Ph huynh nn quan st xem m trng long hay c mu xanh, vng c v cn a tr ti ngay c s y t  c cc bc s thm khm v iu tr.</p>\r\n<h2><i>- Ch  dinh dng v thc hin ch nh ca bc s</i></h2>\r\n<p>Tr ho c m th cha m cn ch  n<a class=\"link-inline-content\" title=\"dinh dng \" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.vn/lam-gi-de-cai-thien-tinh-trang-suy-dinh-duong-cua-tre-em-169175764.htm\" data-rel=\"follow\">dinh dn</a>g ca tr. Cho tr n lm nhiu ba, n long. Nn b sung thc phm giu vitamin C, vitamin A, km v st cng cc loi dng cht khc. Nn cho tr n nhng mn c nhiu nc, d tiu, nhng c y  dng cht nh cho, sa... cn hn ch nhng mn n ch bin c nhiu m nh  chin, xo...</p>\r\n<h2><i>- Khng t  dng thuc tr ho, thuc tiu m khi cha c ch nh ca bc s</i></h2>\r\n<p>Ma lnh cn gi m c th tr, c bit l cc vng c, bn chn; m bo mi trng sng v hc tp ca tr lun sch s, hn ch khi bi v vi khun tn cng tr; m bo  m trong nh  mc  ph hp; Khi tr ng nn nng cao gi  gip tr d th hn v ng ngon gic hn. Cht lng gic ng m bo s gp phn nng cao sc  khng cho tr.</p>\r\n<div id=\"ObjectBoxContent_1703493010762\" class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode alignCenter\" data-back=\"#FFFBF2\" data-border=\"#F2D1AA\" data-text-color=\"#333333\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Ho cng l triu chng ca nhiu nguyn nhn gm: H hp; Tim mch (suy tim tri); Tiu ha (do tro ngc d dy thc qun); Tc dng ph ca thuc; Tm l</p>\r\n<p>V phn loi c ho khan v ho c m. Trong , ho khan l ho khng c m do vim mi hng, vim amidan, vim tai gia, nhim siu vi hay tr ht phi tc nhn gy kch ng (khi thuc l, phn hoa, mi kh chu). i vi ho c m l khi ho c tit nhiu m c hoc long do vim tiu ph qun, vim ph qun, vim phi, lao phi, hen suyn.</p>\r\n<p>V mc  ho, nu tr ho di 3 tun c xem l ho cp tnh; t 3 - 8 tun l ho bn cp tnh; trn 8 tun tr ln l ho mn tnh.</p>\r\n<p>Hin thuc  iu tr ho chia thnh 3 loi: Antitussive (chng ho); Protussive (h tr ho) v thuc ho tho dc. Da vo c tnh ca tng loi thuc v tnh trng bnh ca tr, bc s s c phng hng ch nh.</p>\r\n<p> trnh cc h ly khng mong mun, bc s Khi khuyn co: Ph huynh khng nn t  dng thuc cho tr nu cha c s cho php ca y bc s. a tr n c s y t  c thm khm, chn on v iu tr thch hp.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 10, '2024-01-05 01:08:09', 674, '', '2024-01-05 02:06:41', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:08:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 5, 1, '', '', 1, 1, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xre