(10, 82, '14 loi thc phm gip gim m mu cao, bo v tim', '14-lo-i-th-c-ph-m-giup-gi-m-m-mau-cao-b-o-v-tim', '<p><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"Ch  n ung khng lnh mnh gy m mu cao.\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/mo-mau-cao-17034816389221458711432.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img id=\"img_663612865159598080\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"14 loi thc phm gip gim m mu cao, bo v tim- nh 1.\" src=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/thumb_w/640/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/mo-mau-cao-17034816389221458711432.jpg\" alt=\"14 loi thc phm gip gim m mu cao, bo v tim- nh 1.\" width=\"341\" height=\"226\" data-adbro-processed=\"true\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/mo-mau-cao-17034816389221458711432.jpg\" /></a></p>\r\n', '\r\n<h2 class=\"detail-sapo\" data-role=\"sapo\">SKS - M mu cao hay ri lon chuyn ha lipid mu (cholesterol mu cao) l mt trong nhng yu t dn n x va ng mch v nhiu bin chng tim mch nguy him. Ch  n ung c th ng mt vai tr quan trng trong vic gip qun l m mu cao.</h2>\r\n<h2 class=\"detail-sapo\" data-role=\"sapo\"><b>1.<a class=\"seo-suggest-link\" title=\"M mu cao khi no cn iu tr ?\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.vn/mo-mau-cao-khi-nao-can-dieu-tri-169230803120024054.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">M mu cao</a>t thi quen n ung v sinh hot</b></h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-content afcbc-body\" data-role=\"content\">\r\n<div class=\"toc-list-headings VCSortableInPreviewMode alignRight\" data-heading-select=\"h2, h3\" data-style=\"align-right\">\r\n<div class=\"toc-title\">NI DUNG</div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"toc-level toc-level-0\"><a href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.vn/14-loai-thuc-pham-giup-giam-mo-mau-cao-bao-ve-tim-169231225123531992.htm#1-mo-mau-cao-tu-thoi-quen-an-uong-va-sinh-hoat\">1. M mu cao t thi quen n ung v sinh hot</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"toc-level toc-level-0\"><a href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.vn/14-loai-thuc-pham-giup-giam-mo-mau-cao-bao-ve-tim-169231225123531992.htm#2-14-loai-thuc-pham-ban-co-the-an-de-giup-giam-mo-mau-cao\">2. 14 loi thc phm bn c th n  gip gim m mu cao</a></li>\r\n<li class=\"toc-level toc-level-0\"><a href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.vn/14-loai-thuc-pham-giup-giam-mo-mau-cao-bao-ve-tim-169231225123531992.htm#3-cac-thuc-pham-can-tranh\">3. Cc thc phm cn trnh</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Hu ht mi ngi b m mu cao do nguyn nhn t ch  n ung, sinh hot thiu lnh mnh khin cholesterol tch t trong mu v gy nh hng n tim mch.</p>\r\n<p>Cholesterol LDL l cholesterol \"xu\" v n khin cht bo tch t trong mch mu. HDL, hay cholesterol \"tt\", gip loi b cholesterol khi c th qua gan. Mc cholesterol HDL cao c th lm gim nguy c mc cc vn  v tim v<a class=\"seo-suggest-link\" title=\"Phn bit nhi mu c tim v t qu\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.vn/phan-biet-nhoi-mau-co-tim-va-dot-quy-169231219083454163.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">t qu</a>.</p>\r\n<p><i>Ch  n ung khng lnh mnh:</i></p>\r\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\r\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"Ch  n ung khng lnh mnh gy m mu cao.\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/mo-mau-cao-17034816389221458711432.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img id=\"img_663612865159598080\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"14 loi thc phm gip gim m mu cao, bo v tim- nh 1.\" src=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/thumb_w/640/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/mo-mau-cao-17034816389221458711432.jpg\" alt=\"14 loi thc phm gip gim m mu cao, bo v tim- nh 1.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-adbro-processed=\"true\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/mo-mau-cao-17034816389221458711432.jpg\" /></a>\r\n<div id=\"adbro\" class=\"adbro-animated adbro-md\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-surf\">\r\n<div class=\"adbro-surf__container\">\r\n<div class=\"adbro-surf__img adbro-surf__img--1\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-surf__img adbro-surf__img--2\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-surf__img adbro-surf__img--3\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-surf__img adbro-surf__img--4\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-surf__text\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-surf__logo\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-surf__btn\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<img src=\"https://bs.serving-sys.com/Serving/adServer.bs?cn=display&amp;c=19&amp;pli=1079857318&amp;gdpr=${GDPR}&amp;gdpr_consent=${GDPR_CONSENT_68}&amp;us_privacy=${US_PRIVACY}&amp;adid=1092111537&amp;ebaddid=ba3964b7d5df43b8bc0bf13d6dfa37a6&amp;ord=1703569115576\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" />\r\n<div id=\"adbro-info-handler\" class=\"adbro-icon\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-close\" data-block-reason=\"0\" data-block=\"false\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-link\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\r\n<p data-placeholder=\"Nhp ch thch nh\">Ch  n ung khng lnh mnh gy m mu cao.</p>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<div>\r\n<div id=\"adbro-bottom\" class=\"adbro-bottom adbro-satellite adbro-moat-beacon\">\r\n<div class=\"adbro-slider\">\r\n<div class=\"adbro-grid\">\r\n<div class=\"adbro-close\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-grid__top\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-grid__list\">\r\n<div class=\"adbro-grid__item adbro-grid__item--wide\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-slider__wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"adbro-slider__frame\">\r\n<div class=\"adbro-slider__list\" data-carousel-autoplay=\"true\">\r\n<div class=\"adbro-grid__slide-img adbro-grid__slide-img--1\"></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"adbro-grid__slide-img adbro-grid__slide-img--2\"></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"adbro-grid__slide-img adbro-grid__slide-img--3\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-grid__img\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-grid__arrow\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"adbro-grid__btn\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>n qu nhiu thc phm cha nhiu cht bo xu, kh tiu ha nh: tht , kem, b, sa, bnh ngt, ph mai, gan, cc loi ni tng ng vt, cc loi thc phm ch bin np vo c th lng ln cholesterol xu. Nhng cholesterol xu ny kh c th c c th hp th v chuyn ha hon ton nn vn c lu hnh trong mu lng, t  gy hnh thnh mng<a class=\"seo-suggest-link\" title=\"n trng nhiu d x va mch mu\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.vn/an-trung-nhieu-de-xo-vua-mach-mau-16920496.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">x va mch mu</a>.</p>\r\n<p><i>Thi quen li vn ng:</i></p>\r\n<div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode alignRight\" data-relatednewsboxtype=\"type-1\" data-style=\"align-right\">\r\n<div class=\"kbwscwl-relatedbox type-1 suckhoedoisong\">\r\n<ul class=\"kbwscwlr-list\">\r\n<li class=\"kbwscwlrl\" data-avatar=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2022/6/15/a-va-bi-tang-mo-mau-nen-kieng-gi-16552934343961483602841-23-0-429-650-crop-16552934436362014243469.png\" data-date=\"16/06/2022 10:30\" data-id=\"169220615185757453\" data-title=\"Ngi b bnh m mu cao phi king hon ton cht bo?\" data-url=\"/nguoi-bi-benh-mo-mau-cao-phai-kieng-hoan-toan-chat-beo-169220615185757453.htm\"><a class=\"kbwscwlrl-thumb link-callout\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.vn/nguoi-bi-benh-mo-mau-cao-phai-kieng-hoan-toan-chat-beo-169220615185757453.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img title=\"14 loi thc phm gip gim m mu cao, bo v tim- nh 2.\" src=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2022/6/15/a-va-bi-tang-mo-mau-nen-kieng-gi-16552934343961483602841-23-0-429-650-crop-16552934436362014243469.png\" alt=\"Ngi b bnh m mu cao phi king hon ton cht bo?\" /></a>\r\n<h4 class=\"kbwscwlrl-title clearfix\"><a class=\"title link-callout\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.vn/nguoi-bi-benh-mo-mau-cao-phai-kieng-hoan-toan-chat-beo-169220615185757453.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ngi b bnh m mu cao phi king hon ton cht bo?</a><a class=\"kbwscwlrl-next link-callout\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.vn/nguoi-bi-benh-mo-mau-cao-phai-kieng-hoan-toan-chat-beo-169220615185757453.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span class=\"text\">C NGAY</span></a></h4>\r\n<div class=\"arrow-wrap\"></div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Ngoi ch  n ung km lnh mnh th nhng ngi ngi, nm qu nhiu, li vn ng th thao c nguy c m mu cao hn nhng ngi sinh hot th thao thng xuyn. Nhng ngi b m mu cao nn vn ng hng ngy  c th tiu hao bt lng cht bo d tha trong c th.</p>\r\n<p><i>Thi quen ht thuc:</i></p>\r\n<p>Nhiu ngi cho rng, ht thuc ch gy hi n phi do cc ha cht c hi c trong thuc, tuy nhin cc nghin cu  ch ra, khi thuc l cn gy gim cholesterol tt trong mu. T  dn n mt cn bng cholesterol vi lng cholesterol xu chim u th, nguy c<a class=\"seo-suggest-link\" title=\"Duy tr nng  ng huyt  vng an ton  trnh bin chng mch mu\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.vn/duy-tri-nong-do-duong-huyet-o-vung-an-toan-de-tranh-bien-chung-mach-mau-1696403.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">bin chng mch mu</a>v vy cng cao hn.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"2-14-loai-thuc-pham-ban-co-the-an-de-giup-giam-mo-mau-cao\"><b>2. 14 loi thc phm bn c th n  gip gim m mu cao</b></h2>\r\n<p><b>2.1 C tm</b></p>\r\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\r\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"C tm giu cht x gip gim m mu cao.\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/ca-tim-1703481904761347702179.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img id=\"img_663613979669229568\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"14 loi thc phm gip gim m mu cao, bo v tim- nh 3.\" src=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/thumb_w/640/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/ca-tim-1703481904761347702179.jpg\" alt=\"14 loi thc phm gip gim m mu cao, bo v tim- nh 3.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/ca-tim-1703481904761347702179.jpg\" /></a></div>\r\n<figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\r\n<p data-placeholder=\"Nhp ch thch nh\">C tm giu cht x gip gim m mu cao.</p>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>Hip hi Tim mch Hoa K (AHA) lu , cht x gip ci thin mc cholesterol trong mu, lm gim nguy c pht trin bnh tim, t qu, bo ph,<a class=\"seo-suggest-link\" title=\"B sung protein trc ba n c th gip kim sot bnh i tho ng type 2\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.vn/bo-sung-protein-truoc-bua-an-co-the-giup-kiem-soat-benh-dai-thao-duong-type-2-169220530164716141.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">bnh i tho ng type 2</a>.</p>\r\n<p>C tm l mt loi thc phm giu cht dinh dng, cha mt lng ln vitamin, khong cht v cht x vi t calo.</p>\r\n<p><i>Mt cc (82 gram) c tm sng cha:</i></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Lng calo: 20</li>\r\n<li>Carb: 5g</li>\r\n<li>Cht x: 3g</li>\r\n<li>Cht m: 1g</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>C tm cng cha mangan, folate: 5% RDI, kali, vitamin K, vitamin C v mt lng nh cht dinh dng khc, bao gm niacin, magie v ng.</p>\r\n<p>Nh hm lng cht chng oxy ha, mt s nghin cu cho thy c tm c th gip gim nguy c mc bnh tim.</p>\r\n<p>Theo nghin cu, ngi n c tm c mc cholesterol LDL v cht bo trung tnh thp hn, hai du hiu trong mu c th dn n tng nguy c mc bnh tim khi tng cao. Cc nghin cu khc  chng minh rng c tm c th c tc dng<a class=\"seo-suggest-link\" title=\"Mo ct gim lng mui  bo v tim\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.vn/meo-cat-giam-luong-muoi-de-bao-ve-tim-169137980.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">bo v tim</a>.</p>\r\n<p><b>2.2 u bp</b></p>\r\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode small-img\">\r\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"u bp.\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/dau-bap-1703481980125808737868.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img id=\"img_663614295244173312\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"14 loi thc phm gip gim m mu cao, bo v tim- nh 4.\" src=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/dau-bap-1703481980125808737868.jpg\" alt=\"14 loi thc phm gip gim m mu cao, bo v tim- nh 4.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/dau-bap-1703481980125808737868.jpg\" /></a></div>\r\n<figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\r\n<p data-placeholder=\"Nhp ch thch nh\">u bp.</p>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>Cc nh nghin cu  pht hin ra rng mt loi gel trong u bp gi l cht nhy c th gip gim cholesterol bng cch lin kt vi n trong qu trnh tiu ha. iu ny gip cholesterol ri khi c th qua bi tit, thay v hp th vo c th.</p>\r\n<p><i>Mt cc (100g) u bp th cha:</i></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Lng calo: 33</li>\r\n<li>Carb: 7g</li>\r\n<li>Cht m: 2g</li>\r\n<li>Cht bo: 0g</li>\r\n<li>Cht x: 3g</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>u bp l ngun cung cp vitamin C v K1 tuyt vi. Vitamin C l mt cht dinh dng ha tan trong nc gp phn vo chc nng min dch tng th, trong khi vitamin K1 l mt loi vitamin tan trong cht bo.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, u bp c lng calo v carbs thp, ng thi cha mt s protein v cht x. Nhiu loi tri cy v rau qu thiu protein, iu ny khin u bp c phn c o. n  cht m c lin quan n li ch trong vic kim sot cn nng, kim sot lng ng trong mu, cu trc xng v khi lng c bp.</p>\r\n<p>Mc cholesterol cao c lin quan n nguy c mc bnh tim cao hn. Mt li ch khc cho tim ca u bp l hm lng polyphenol. Mt nghin cu ko di 4 nm  1.100 ngi cho thy nhng ngi n ch  n giu polyphenol c du hiu vim lin quan n bnh tim thp hn.</p>\r\n<p><b>2.3 To</b></p>\r\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\r\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"To.\" href=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/tao-17034820272962106560347.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img id=\"img_663614493552533504\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"14 loi thc phm gip gim m mu cao, bo v tim- nh 5.\" src=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/thumb_w/640/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/tao-17034820272962106560347.jpg\" alt=\"14 loi thc phm gip gim m mu cao, bo v tim- nh 5.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https://suckhoedoisong.qltns.mediacdn.vn/324455921873985536/2023/12/25/tao-17034820272962106560347.jpg\" /></a></div>\r\n<figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\r\n<p data-placeholder=\"Nhp ch thch nh\">To.</p>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 10, '2024-01-05 01:08:33', 674, '', '2024-01-06 14:57:25', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:08:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 14, 0, '', '', 1, 1, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 1, '*', '', ''),
(11, 83, 'Tn hiu vui ca du lch Kin Giang', 'tin-hi-u-vui-c-a-du-l-ch-kien-giang', '<p><img src=\"images/dulich.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<h2 class=\"title-italic\">(KGO) - Cc hot ng du lch trn a bn Kin Giang  dn hi phc vi nhiu tn hiu tch cc.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"newscontent\">\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid\"><strong>QUC T NH GI CAO</strong></div>\r\n<p>Du lch Kin Giang tip tc c nhiu t chc du lch uy tn trn th gii xp hng cao  khu vc, chu  v th gii nh tp ch du lch Cond Nast Traveler (M) vinh danh Ph Quc nm trong top nhng hn o tuyt vi nht nm 2023; ring hng mc c s lu tr, Ph Quc c 5 i din c trao gii dn u khu vc ny.</p>\r\n<p>Trong khi , cng vin nc Aquatopia Water Park Ph Quc vt qua nhiu i th mnh t Trung Quc, Hn Quc, Singapore  nhn gii cng vin nc hng u chu  Tp ch du lch The Travel xp Ph Quc 3/17 hn o c chi ph du lch r nht th gii.</p>\r\n<p>Nhng thng cui nm 2023, Ph Quc lin tip n cc chuyn bay quc t a du khch n tham quan, ngh dng. y l lot tn hiu khi sc nh du s phc hi du lch t th trng khch quc t. Cc hng hng khng ln ca Hn Quc lin tip tng cng nhiu ng bay mi n Ph Quc. Cc hng thng tn ln ca x s kim chi cho rng Ph Quc l im n du lch m gia nh, bn b v cc cp i c th tn hng.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/images/2023/12/01/083446kgo_20231201_M%E1%BB%99t%20g%C3%B3c%20x%C3%A3%20%C4%91%E1%BA%A3o%20H%C3%B2n%20S%C6%A1n%20(Ki%C3%AAn%20H%E1%BA%A3i).webp\" alt=\"083446kgo_20231201_Mt gc x o Hn Sn (Kin Hi)\" /><img src=\"images/dulich.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>Mt gc x o Hn Sn, huyn Kin Hi.</em></p>\r\n<p>ng Yong Sung Ok - Trng Phng khu vc ng Nam  Cng ty du lch Hanatour (Hn Quc) nhn nh: Vit Nam, trong  c Ph Quc l im n c tm kim v ph bin nht vi du khch Hn Quc thi gian gn y do v tr a l gn nhau, c nhiu ng bay, gi v my bay r vi ngi Hn Quc. Ngoi ra, Vit Namcn hp dn du khch quc t bi chnh sch min hon ton th thc, thi hn tm tr 30 ngy.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_1\">\r\n<div id=\"ats-insert_ads-0-wrapper\" class=\"insert_ads insert_ads-2 show_advertisement rendered\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>ADVERTISEMENT</p>\r\n<div id=\"ats-insert_ads-0\" class=\"ats-slot\" data-google-query-id=\"CND_gpS0rIMDFcPxTAIdH6EGJA\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Gim c S Du lch Kin GiangBi Quc Thi cho bit vic khch quc t tr li Ph Quc ng mt phn t s nh gi khch quan cacc t chc, tp ch du lch uy tn hng u th gii v Ph Quc. Gn y nht, Travel Lemming (Hoa K) xp Ph Quc ng th 6 trong danh sch 50 im n du lch hng u th gii nm 2024. iu ny cho thy Ph Quc l im n c du khch a chung t v p,  cun ht v sn phm, cht lng dch v.</p>\r\n<p><strong>TO THM SC BT</strong></p>\r\n<p>Gn y, ti Hn Sn, huyn Kin Hi, du khch thch th n check in im du lch c kin trc kh c o - Flyup resort. y c xem l cng trnh gp phn lm thay i din mo du lch x hn khi thu ht lng ln du khch.</p>\r\n<p>ng Trn Hong Sn - du khch n t TP. Pleiku (Gia Lai) cho bit: Ti gh Hn Sn sau chuyn i Nam Du. Ti bt ng khi Hn Sn c u t mt c s lu tr rt p v khc bit. Hn Sn vn c li th v cnh quan, cn c ngun nhn lc du lch nhit tnh, hiu khch. Ti ngh ni ny ch cn gi gi cc dch v th thng hiu Hn Sn cn vn xa.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/images/2023/12/01/083433kgo_20231201_c%C3%A2u%20c%C3%A1%20gi%E1%BA%A3i%20tr%C3%AD%20tr%C3%AAn%20bi%E1%BB%83n%20R%E1%BA%A1ch%20V%E1%BA%B9m%20(TP.%20Ph%C3%BA%20Qu%E1%BB%91c).webp\" alt=\"083433kgo_20231201_cu c gii tr trn bin Rch Vm (TP\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>Khch du lch tham gia tour cu c gii tr trn bin Rch Vm (TP. Ph Quc).</em></p>\r\n<p>Theo Hip hi Du lch tnh Kin Giang, nm 2023 ngnh du lch chu nh hng nng ca suy thoi kinh t nhng cc hot ng du lch trn a bn Kin Giang dn hi phc vi nhiu tn hiu tch cc.Ch tiu v lng khch, doanh thu  vt k hoch nm; ring du khch quc t vt n 63,8%.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_2\"></div>\r\n<p>Theo ng Trn Quc Khnh - Ch tch Hip hi Du lch tnh,  gp phn thc y du lch phc hi, hip hi cnhiu chng trnh qung b, xc tin du lch Kin Giang n cc th trng du lch trong v ngoi nc. Hip hi ku gi cc thnh vin to sn phm du lch mi, nng cht lng sn phm du lch.</p>\r\n<p>Theo , ti Ph Quc, cc doanh nghip a vo khai thc nhiu sn phm du lch mi, ng cp nh Cu Hn, du thuyn 5 sao Nautilus v hng lot chng trnh kch cu du lch, chui l hi gii tr ng cp quc t thu ht lng ln du khch vui chi, khm ph.</p>\r\n<p>Theo S Du lch Kin Giang, ngnh du lch s phi hp n v lin quan, doanh nghip tng cng kch cu du lch; nghin cu,  xut chnh sch u i u t, to mi trng u t kinh doanh du lch thun li, thng thong cho doanh nghip.</p>\r\n<p>Song song , Kin Giang tp trung khai thc m hnh du lch kinh t v m qua cc hot ng biu din vn ha, ngh thut,m thc ti Ph Quc, Rch Gi, H Tin, Kin Hi</p>\r\n<p>Ring Ph Quc s pht trin thm cc nhm sn phm, dch v gn khm ph nt vn ha cng ng dn c  hai phng Dng ng v An Thi; nghin cu xy dng tuyn ph i b kt hp mua sm, m thc</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_3\"></div>\r\n<div>Tng lt du khch n Kin Giang nm 2023 c t 8.534.993 lt, tng 15,3% so cng k, vt 2,8% k hoch nm; trong  du khch quc t c n 573.272 lt, tng 203,3% so cng k nm 2022, vt 63,8% k hoch nm; tng doanh thu t du lch c t 17.479 t ng, tng 65,1% so cng k, vt 34,5% k hoch nm 2023.</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 11, '2024-01-05 01:08:57', 674, '', '2024-01-05 02:11:31', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:08:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 8, 2, '', '', 1, 5, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 1, '*', '', ''),
(12, 84, 'Nhiu quyt nh quan trng v pht trin kinh t - x hi nm 2024', 'nhi-u-quy-t-d-nh-quan-tr-ng-v-phat-tri-n-kinh-t-xa-h-i-nam-2024', '<header class=\"detail__header\"><img src=\"images/kgphattrioen.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"images/z5008035318071-ac2a711e0bc725b40dc9a761abffdf8f.jpg\" alt=\"\" />', '\r\n<h2 class=\"detail__summary\">Kinhtedothi - Ngy 25/12, HND tnh Kin Giang kha X, nhim k 2021-2026 t chc k hp th 20  xem xem xt, nh gi tnh hnh thc hin ngh quyt ca HND tnh v nhim v pht trin kinh t- x hi nm 2023 v  ra nhim v pht trin nm 2024.</h2>\r\n<h2 class=\"detail__summary\">Theo , ti K hp ny, HND tnh Kin Giang xem xt, quyt nh 4 ni dung quan trng gm: Xem xt, nh gi tnh hnh thc hin ngh quyt ca HND tnh Kin Giang v nhim v pht trin KT - XH nm 2023 v k hoch pht trin kinh t - x hi nm 2024; Cc bo co ca Thng trc HND, cc ban HND, UBND, cc c quan t php tnh Kin Giangnm 2023 v nhim v nm 2024.</h2>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"detail__content-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"detail__content\">\r\n<figure class=\"image-wrap align-center-image\"><img src=\"https://static.kinhtedothi.vn/w960/images/upload/2023/12/25/z5008035318071-ac2a711e0bc725b40dc9a761abffdf8f.jpg\" alt=\"To&amp;agrave;n cnh k hp th 20 HND kh&amp;oacute;a X nhim k 2021-2026. (nh Hu Tun)\" data-original=\"https://static.kinhtedothi.vn/images/upload//2023/12/25/z5008035318071-ac2a711e0bc725b40dc9a761abffdf8f.jpg\" />\r\n<figcaption class=\"image-caption\">Ton cnh k hp th 20 HND kha X nhim k 2021-2026. (nh Hu Tun)</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>ng thi, nghe y ban Mt trn T quc Vit Nam tnh Kin Giangthng bo tnh hnh hot ng ca Mt trn tham gia xy dng chnh quyn nm 2023, nhim v nm 2024; bo co gim st kt qu gii quyt kin ngh ca c tri trc v sau K hp thng l gia nm 2023. Xem xt cc t trnh ca Thng trc HND, UBND tnh Kin Giang; gii trnh, cht vn v tr li cht vn; thng qua cc ngh quyt ca HND trnh K hp.</p>\r\n<p>Nm 2023, tnh hnh KT - XH nm 2023 ca tnh Kin Giang tip tc n nh v pht trin kh; c 23/24 ch tiu t v vt k hoch, cn li 1 ch tiu t trn 90% k hoch. Tc  tng trng kinh t t 6,79%. Thu ngn sch vt ch tiu  ra.</p>\r\n<p>Tng khch du lch trong nm c n trn 8,5 triu lt khch, tng 15,6% (khch quc t, tng 177%), tng doanh thu tng 65% so cng k. Tng thu ngn sch hn 15.120 t ng, vt 24% k hoch, tng 26,8% so cng k.</p>\r\n<p>ng Mai Vn Hunh, Ch tch HND tnh Kin Giang cho bit, ti K hp ny, HND tnh Kin Giangxem xt, cho  kin i vi 48 ni dung bo co, t trnh, d tho ngh quyt; c nhiu ni dung quan trng tc ng n s pht trin KT - XH, quc phng, an ninh, m bo an sinh x hi ca a phng. ng thi,  ngh cc v i biu pht huy dn ch, nu cao tinh thn trch nhim, tch cc tham gia tho lun, ng gp nhiu  kin cht lng cc ni dung trnh K hp.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 11, '2024-01-05 01:09:19', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:52:28', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:09:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 6, 1, '', '', 1, 2, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 1, '*', '', '');
