(13, 85, 'Kin Giang phc hi, n nh v pht trin kinh t - x hi', 'kien-giang-ph-c-h-i-n-d-nh-va-phat-tri-n-kinh-t-xa-h-i', '<p><img src=\"images/phatbieu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"images/1mvhuynh-6223.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>(PLVN) - Nm 2023, tnh Kin Giang c quy m tng sn phm trn a bn (GRDP) c t 73.377 t ng, vt 0,68% k hoch, tc  tng trng 6,79%.</p>\r\n<div class=\"article__body cms-body \">\r\n<p>Ngy 25/12, HND tnh Kin Giang kho X, nhim k 2021 - 2026, khai mc k hp 20 (k hp cui nm 2023) tng kt tnh hnh ngh quyt ca HND tnh v nhim v pht trin kinh t - x hi nm 2023 v xem xt gii quyt mt s ni dung thuc thm quyn.</p>\r\n<table class=\"picture\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"pic\"><img class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" title=\"ng Mai Vn Hunh - Ph b th Tnh u Kin Giang, Ch tch HND tnh Kin Giang - pht biu khai mc k hp 20 (k hp cui nm) ca HND tnh Kin Giang kho X, nhim k 2021-2026 (nh: Khnh Thu)\" src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/zshvwyvobvhvim/2023_12_25/1mvhuynh-6223.jpg\" alt=\"ng Mai Vn Hunh - Ph b th Tnh u Kin Giang, Ch tch HND tnh Kin Giang - pht biu khai mc k hp 20 (k hp cui nm) ca HND tnh Kin Giang kho X, nhim k 2021-2026 (nh: Khnh Thu)\" width=\"840\" height=\"560\" data-height=\"1707\" data-image-id=\"947668\" data-src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/zshvwyvobvhvim/2023_12_25/1mvhuynh-6223.jpg\" data-width=\"2560\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"caption\">\r\n<p>ng Mai Vn Hunh - Ph b th Tnh u Kin Giang, Ch tch HND tnh Kin Giang - pht biu khai mc k hp 20 (k hp cui nm) ca HND tnh Kin Giang kho X, nhim k 2021-2026 (nh: Khnh Thu)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>ng Nguyn Thanh Nhn - Ph Ch tch UBND tnh Kin Giang - cho bit: Nm 2023, tnh Kin Giang c quy m tng sn phm trn a bn tnh (GRDP) c t 73.377 t ng, vt 0,68% k hoch, tc  tng trng 6,79% (k hoch 6,5%).</p>\r\n<div class=\"ads_middle\"></div>\r\n<p>Nng - lm - thy sn  a phng tng 2,96%; cng nghip - xy dng, tng 8,36%; thng mi - dch v, tng 10,02%; thu sn phm tr tr cp sn phm, tng 5,95%; cng nghip - xy dng, chim 20,53%<em>;</em>dch v chim 37,53% v thu nhp khu, thu sn phm tr tr cp sn phm chim 4,92%<em>.</em>GRDP bnh qun u ngi  a phng c t 73,74 triu ng, tng 3,85% k hoch.</p>\r\n<p>c bit, nm 2023, tnh Kin Giang c n trn 8,5 triu lt khch, vt 2,8% k hoch, tng 15% so cng k. Ring khch du lch quc t t 573.000 lt, vt 63,8% k hoch, tng doanh thu du lch gn 17.500 t ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ads_middle\"></div>\r\n<table class=\"picture\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"pic\"><img class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" title=\"ng Nguyn Thanh Nhn - Ph Ch tch UBND tnh Kin Giang - cho bit nm 2023, Kin Giang phc hi v pht trin kinh t mnh m. (nh: Khnh Thu)\" src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/zshvwyvobvhvim/2023_12_25/1ngthanhnhan-3602.jpg\" alt=\"ng Nguyn Thanh Nhn - Ph Ch tch UBND tnh Kin Giang - cho bit nm 2023, Kin Giang phc hi v pht trin kinh t mnh m. (nh: Khnh Thu)\" width=\"840\" height=\"647\" data-height=\"987\" data-image-id=\"947669\" data-src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/zshvwyvobvhvim/2023_12_25/1ngthanhnhan-3602.jpg\" data-width=\"1280\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"caption\">\r\n<p>ng Nguyn Thanh Nhn - Ph Ch tch UBND tnh Kin Giang - cho bit nm 2023, Kin Giang phc hi v pht trin kinh t mnh m. (nh: Khnh Thu)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>ng Nhn cho bit thm: Kinh t tuy c phc hi v tng trng kh; c cu kinh t chuyn dch ng hng, nhng cn chm. Do ,  pht trin kinh t x hi trong nm 2024, a phng tip tc tp trung thc hin cc chnh sch gp phn kim sot lm pht, n nh nn kinh t; y mnh gii ngn vn u t cng, to nn tng cho pht trin nhanh v bn vng. Bn cnh , tnh Kin Giang thc hin ng b, hiu qu cng tc ci cch hnh chnh, ci thin mi trng kinh doanh. To iu kin pht trin cc thnh phn kinh t, nng cao nng lc cnh tranh trn a bn tnh.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, tnh Kin Giang phn u s dng hiu qu ngun nhn lc, nht l ngun nhn lc cht lng cao, gn vi y mnh i mi sng to, ng dng v pht trin mnh m khoa hc, cng ngh. Ch ng ng ph hiu qu vi bin i kh hu, phng, chng thin tai, pht trin sn xut, n nh cuc sng ngi dn, ng Nhn ni.</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 11, '2024-01-05 01:09:40', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:52:51', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:09:40', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 6, 0, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 1, '*', '', ''),
(14, 86, 'Thu dung ngi lang thang xin n  TP.HCM: \'Ti con phi xin c 500.000 ng\'', 'thu-dung-ngu-i-lang-thang-xin-an-tp-hcm-t-i-con-ph-i-xin-du-c-500-000-d-ng', '<p><img src=\"images/benh-vien-da-chien-4-11-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<h2 class=\"detail-sapo\" data-role=\"sapo\">Trong 2 thng 11 - 12.2023, PV<i>Thanh Nin</i>c tri nghim thc t theo chn mt s t cng tc  TP.HCM  thu dung ngi lang thang, xin n  xc minh a v cc c s h tr x hi ca nh nc.</h2>\r\n<div id=\"zone-k911czvz\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-cmain\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-content afcbc-body\" data-io-article-url=\"https://thanhnien.vn/thu-dung-nguoi-lang-thang-xin-an-o-tphcm-tui-con-phai-xin-duoc-500000-dong-185231228141759782.htm\" data-role=\"content\">\r\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"3 a tr xin n ti nt giao thng ng Vn Cng - Mai Ch Th c a v xc minh, sau  c a vo Trung tm h tr x hi TP.HCM\" href=\"https://images2.thanhnien.vn/528068263637045248/2023/12/24/edit-1d-1703392601306787900173.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img id=\"img_663239433538162688\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"Thu dung ngi lang thang xin n  TP.HCM: \'Ti con phi xin c 500.000 ng\'- nh 1.\" src=\"https://images2.thanhnien.vn/thumb_w/640/528068263637045248/2023/12/24/edit-1d-1703392601306787900173.png\" alt=\"Thu dung ngi lang thang xin n  TP.HCM: \'Ti con phi xin c 500.000 ng\'- nh 1.\" width=\"844\" height=\"658\" data-adbro-processed=\"true\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https://images2.thanhnien.vn/528068263637045248/2023/12/24/edit-1d-1703392601306787900173.png\" /></a></div>\r\n<div data-check-position=\"body_start\"></div>\r\n<p>15 gi 30 ngy 30.11, PV<i>Thanh Nin</i>theo t cng tc TP.Th c (thnh vin t gm i din Phng L-TB-XH TP.Th c, Cng an TP.Th c, Trung tm h tr<a class=\"VCCAutoLink link-inline-content\" title=\"x hi\" href=\"https://thanhnien.vn/thoi-su/dan-sinh.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-id-autolink=\"8928\">x hi</a>TP.HCM) ro qua nhiu tuyn ng trn a bn  tp trung<a class=\"seo-suggest-link\" title=\"TP.HCM m t cao im tp trung tr em, ngi lang thang xin n\" href=\"https://thanhnien.vn/tphcm-mo-dot-cao-diem-tap-trung-tre-em-nguoi-lang-thang-xin-an-185231228080651752.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ngi lang thang</a>, xin n.</p>\r\n<div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" data-eid=\"\" data-embed-code=\"\" data-embed-json=\"\" data-id=\"55ebc6e2-c3b1-4a62-93c4-b2aed9c16bec\" data-oa=\"thanhnien\" data-style=\"align-center\"></div>\r\n<p>16 gi ngy 30.11, ti nt giao thng ng dn ln cu vt Ct Li (on khi va  dc cu Rch Chic hng v cu Si Gn) thuc P.An Ph, khi n , c 3 a tr lin chy ra lng ng cha tay<a class=\"seo-suggest-link\" title=\"Xin n\" href=\"https://thanhnien.vn/xin-an.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">xin n</a>. Va thy xe tun tra ca t cng tc dng li th nhng a tr ny tc chy. nh gi on ng c lng xe lu thng ln, s nguy him n tr v ngi tham gia giao thng khc nn t cng tc khng ui theo.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"aries_stage aries_horizontalAxis\">\r\n<div class=\"aries_proscenium aries_hcenter aries_vcenter aries_rollAnimation\">\r\n<div class=\"aries_videoWrapper\">\r\n<div><img width=\"640\" height=\"360\" />\" /&gt;\r\n<div class=\"vidverto vidverto__playlist-wrapper vidverto-type_video vidverto-provider_html5 vidverto__playlist_type_playlist vidverto-ui_enabled vidverto__ratio__16_9 mw-script vidverto-playing mw_size_650 vidverto-hide-controls\" tabindex=\"0\" data-manager=\"ima\">\r\n<div class=\"vidverto-player-container\" tabindex=\"1\">\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__title vidverto__title-hidden\">CORON- A 4k Aerial Film of the Philippines</div>\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__video-wrapper\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__controls\">\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__progress\"><span class=\"vidverto__tooltip\">00:15</span><input autocomplete=\"off\" max=\"100\" type=\"range\" value=\"0\" /><progress class=\"vidverto__progress__buffer\" value=\"50.20376751263708\" max=\"100\"></progress></div>\r\n<button class=\"vidverto__control vidverto__prev-track\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"vidverto__tooltip\">Previous</span></button><button class=\"vidverto__control vidverto__play vidverto__control-pressed\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"label-pressed vidverto__tooltip\">Pause</span></button><button class=\"vidverto__control vidverto__next-track\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"vidverto__tooltip\">Next</span></button>\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__logo default_logo\"><a href=\"https://vidverto.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://ad.vidverto.io/vidverto/player/logo.svg\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__spacer\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__time\">00:13 / 01:54</div>\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__volume\"><button class=\"vidverto__control vidverto__mute vidverto__control-pressed\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"label-pressed vidverto__tooltip\">Unmute</span></button><input autocomplete=\"off\" max=\"1\" type=\"range\" value=\"1\" /></div>\r\n<button class=\"vidverto__control vidverto__settings\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"label-not-pressed vidverto__tooltip\">Settings</span></button><button class=\"vidverto__control vidverto__fullscreen\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"label-not-pressed vidverto__tooltip\">Fullscreen</span></button></div>\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__contextmenu\">\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__contextmenu-item\">Copy video url</div>\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__contextmenu-item\">Play / Pause</div>\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__contextmenu-item\">Mute / Unmute</div>\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__contextmenu-item\">Report a problem</div>\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__contextmenu-item\">Language</div>\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__contextmenu-item\">Share</div>\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__contextmenu-item\">Vidverto Player</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"vidverto__keyboard-hint-container\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"aries_uiElements\">\r\n<div class=\"aries_controlIcon aries_closeControl\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"aries_controlIcon aries_volumeControl aries_mutedSpeaker aries_hidden\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"aries_caption aries_hcenter\">QUNG CO</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n17 gi, khi n nt giao ng ng Vn Cng - Mai Ch Th (P.An Ph), th thy c 3 a tr (2 b gi v 1 b trai) ang ng xin n. Khi thy t cng tc, 1 b gi chy, 2 b cn li ngi khc. T cng tc  a cc em v P.An Ph  xc minh v lm cc th tc  a cc em v Trung tm h tr x hi TP.HCM.\r\n<p></p>\r\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\r\n<p data-placeholder=\"Nhp ch thch nh\">3 a tr xin n ti nt giao thng ng Vn Cng - Mai Ch Th c a v xc minh, sau  c a vo Trung tm h tr x hi TP.HCM</p>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n<div class=\"PhotoCMS_Author\">\r\n<p data-placeholder=\"Nhp tc gi\">TRNG NGHA</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>Qua , bit 3 b l ch em rut ca nhau, b gi ln 10 tui, b trai 7 tui, b gi nh nht 2 tui. B gi 10 tui tn San, ni ting Vit khng rnh, cho hay 3 ch em  ng xin n ti nt giao thng trn t sng,  c ngi i ng cho 200.000 ng v cho n thi im c t cng tc a v phng th vn cha c n ung g.</p>\r\n<p>\"Mi ngy ti con phi xin c 500.000 ng, nu khng  s khng c cho n v s b cha nh. Con ng   xin, lu lu, cha con li ly tin ri i, my con ng  tip, no  tin th thi\", b gi ni v cho hay khng bit nh  u, nhng nu t tm ng v s ra.</p>\r\n<p>Sau khi xc minh lm cc th tc bn giao cho P.An Ph  a cc b v Trung tm h tr x hi TP.HCM, t cng tc TP.Th c tip tc di chuyn, tun tra cc a bn khc.</p>\r\n<div class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\" data-eid=\"\" data-embed-code=\"\" data-embed-json=\"\" data-id=\"0343456e-79de-4e3f-b1fb-4c24625c69b3\" data-oa=\"thanhnien\" data-style=\"align-center\"></div>\r\n<p>Khong 19 gi, t cng tc pht hin 2 ngi gm 1 c ng v 1 ngi n ng ci trn l r cc vt bng, ang ngi di tr n giao thng, on T Ngc Vn - Phm Vn ng (P.Linh Ty) v c ngi i ng cho tin. T cng tc  a 2 ngi ny v tr s cng an phng lm cc th tc xc minh.</p>\r\n<div class=\"dable_placeholder\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 13, '2024-01-05 01:10:14', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:53:12', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:10:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 4, 2, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 1, '*', '', ''),
(15, 87, 'i tuyn Vit Nam hi qun v nhng s vng mt ng tic', 'd-i-tuy-n-vi-t-nam-h-i-quan-va-nh-ng-s-v-ng-m-t-dang-ti-c', '<p><img src=\"images/doi-tuyen-viet-nam-hoi-quan-va-nhung-su-vang-mat-dang-tiec-103720927.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<h2 class=\"detail-sapo fs-17 font-bitter fw-600 text-gray-44 mb-20\">(CLO) HLV Philippe Troussier va cng b danh sch 34 tuyn th Vit Nam chun b cho vng chung kt Asian Cup 2023, trong  ng vai tr ch o vn l s cu th va chinh chin  vng loi th 2 World Cup 2026 cch y hn 1 thng.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content-detail\">\r\n<p>Chiu ngy 25/12, ln u tin Lin on bng  Vit Nam (VFF) cng b danh sch triu tp i tuyn quc gia theo hnh thc trc tuyn trn cc nn tng mng x hi YouTube, TikTok v Facebook. 34 tuyn th  c gi tn, l nhng gng mt c HLV Philippe Troussier v i ng tr l tuyn chn, da trn danh sch s b 50 cu th ng k ln ban t chc Asian Cup 2023 cch y 2 tun.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"expNoEdit\"><a title=\"\"><img src=\"https://congluan-cdn.congluan.vn/files/content/2023/12/26/doi-tuyen-viet-nam-hoi-quan-va-nhung-su-vang-mat-dang-tiec-103720927.jpg\" alt=\"doi tuyen viet nam hoi quan va nhung su vang mat dang tiec hinh 1\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" data-img-mobile=\"undefined\" /></a>\r\n<figcaption>\r\n<p>Tn Ti khng c tn trong danh sch i tuyn Vit Nam chun b cho Asian Cup 2023</p>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>V c bn, phn ln cc cu th trong danh sch ny u va hi qun cch y hn 1 thng cho chin dch vng loi th 2 World Cup 2026, gp Philippines v Iraq. 2 th thnh ng Vn Lm v Nguyn nh Triu tip tc c tn, nhng s i mt vi th thch ln mang tn Nguyn Filip ln u ln tuyn sau khi nhp tch thnh cng. Hng th vn l nhng ci tn quen thuc nh Vit Anh, Vn Thanh, Thanh Bnh, Tun Ti, trong khi hng cng vn do Tun Anh, Tun Hi, Vn Ton, Tin Linh gng gnh.</p>\r\n<p>Tuy nhin, bn danh sch triu tp ca HLV Philippe Troussier vn  li khng t tic nui cho ngi hm m, bi s vng mt ca mt vi ci tn nh Nguyn Vn Quyt, on Vn Hu, Nguyn Cng Phng hay c bit l H Tn Ti - mt trong nhng hu v phi xut sc nht ca bng  Vit Nam hin ti.</p>\r\n<p>V phn Vn Quyt, th qun ca H Ni FC vn ang l chn st ghi nhiu bn thng th 2 trong lch s i tuyn Vit Nam, cn ang thi u. Vn Quyt ghi 16 bn sau 58 ln ra sn, km 2 bn so vi Tin Linh. Ln th 2 lin tip hng ti Asian Cup, lo tng sinh nm 1991 khng gp mt trn tuyn, bi HLV Philippe Troussier mun to c hi cho nhng gng mt tr hn ang c phong  cao nh Tin Linh, nh Bc, Tun Hi hay Vn Ton.</p>\r\n<p>Vic Vn Hu l chuyn xe ln tuyn cng  li nhiu tic nui, ngay c vi chnh HLV Philippe Troussier. Hu v ngi Thi Bnh l nhn t quan trng vi i tuyn Vit Nam, duy tr phong  xut sc  ma gii trc trong hnh trnh cng CLB Cng an H Ni v ch V.League 2023. Tuy nhin, Vn Hu li phi ngh thi u t thng 9 va qua cho ti nay do vn ang iu tr chn thng gt chn.</p>\r\n<p> 2 ln hi qun gn nht, cho lot trn giao hu dp FIFA Days thng 10 v vng loi th 2 World Cup 2026 vo thng 11, Cng Phng u khng c tn ln tuyn. Thay v tr li V.League tm kim c hi ra sn nh ngi ng i Vn Ton, Cng Phng li quyt tm gn b vi Yokohama FC d lin tc b ng l, thm ch cn khng c tn trong danh sch ng k thi u.</p>\r\n<p>Tnh ti nay, cu tin o ca CLB Hong Anh Gia Lai mi c vn vn 2 pht khoc o i bng Nht Bn, trong khi HLV Philippe Troussier lun nhc nh cc cu th cn n lc  tm kin c hi ra sn thi u. Do , vic Cng Phng b gch tn trong danh sch d Asian Cup 2023 thc ra cng khng bt ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"adv ads_id_35\"></div>\r\n<p>Vi trng hp ca Tn Ti, mc d hu v CLB Cng an H Ni duy tr phong  n nh, nhng HLV Philippe Troussier li u tin nhng cu th a nng, c th thi u  nhiu v tr, qua  gip qu trnh xoay tua hoc thay i chin thut tr nn d dng v nhanh chng. Phm Xun Mnh hay cu th tr Trng Tin Anh hin u c th  tt bn cnh phi. Ngoi ra, c Chin cng va c th  hu v ln trung v, hay k c tin v Triu Vit Hng cng tng  hu v ti CLB Hi Phng.</p>\r\n<p>Theo k hoch, i tuyn Vit Nam s hi qun t ngy 28/12 ti H Ni. Ti ngy 5/1/2024, thy tr HLV Philippe Troussier s ln ng sang Qatar tp hun v ti ngy 9/1 th c trn giao hu vi i tuyn Kyrgyzstan.</p>\r\n<p><strong>DANH SCH I TUYN VIT NAM</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Th mn (3):</strong>Nguyn Filip (Cng an H Ni), Nguyn nh Triu (Hi Phng), ng Vn Lm (Bnh nh)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Hu v (12):</strong>V Minh Trng, Qu Ngc Hi (Bnh Dng), Gip Tun Dng, H Vn Cng, Bi Hong Vit Anh, V Vn Thanh (Cng an H Ni),  Duy Mnh, Nguyn Thnh Chung (H Ni), L Ngc Bo,  Thanh Thnh (Bnh nh), Nguyn Thanh Bnh, Phan Tun Ti (Th Cng Viettel)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tin v (13):</strong>Phm Xun Mnh, Nguyn Hai Long,  Hng Dng (H Ni), Nguyn Tun Anh (HAGL), Nguyn Quang Hi, L Phm Thnh Long, Hong Vn Ton (Cng An H Ni), Triu Vit Hng (Hi Phng), Nguyn Hong c, Nguyn c Chin, Trng Tin Anh, Khut Vn Khang (Th Cng Viettel), Nguyn Thi Sn (Thanh Ha)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tin o (6):</strong>Nguyn Vn Ton (Nam nh), Nguyn Tin Linh (Bnh Dng), Phm Tun Hi, Nguyn Vn Tng (H Ni), Nguyn Thanh Nhn (PVF-CAND), Nguyn nh Bc (Qung Nam)</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 13, '2024-01-05 01:10:41', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:53:57', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:10:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_ar