(16, 88, 'Th tng Singapore: Vit Nam t kt qu kinh t n tng', 'th-tu-ng-singapore-vi-t-nam-d-t-k-t-qu-kinh-t-n-tu-ng', '<p><img src=\"images/NQH_0592.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"images/20231223_150549.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<h2 class=\"title-italic\">(KGO) - Sng 18-12, ti Tokyo, Nht Bn, Th tng Phm Minh Chnh  gp Th tng Singapore L Hin Long nhn dp tham d Hi ngh thng nh u tin v \"Cng ng pht thi rng bng 0 chu  (AZEC)\".</h2>\r\n<div class=\"newscontent\">\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid\"><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/images/2023/12/18/165951ttg-viet-sing-1702886402996229441956.webp\" alt=\"165951ttg-viet-sing-1702886402996229441956\" /></div>\r\n<p><em>Th tng Phm Minh Chnh n Th tng Singapore L Hin Long thm chnh thc Vit Nam t ngy 27 n 29-8-2023</em>.</p>\r\n<p>Hai Th tng cng by t hi lng v mt nm 2023 si ni cc hot ng thit thc k nim 50 nm thit lp quan h ngoi giao, 10 nm thit lp quan h i tc Chin lc, c bit l cc chuyn thm v trao i cp cao.</p>\r\n<p>Th tng L Hin Long cng nh gi cao chnh sch i ngoi v iu hnh kinh t ca Chnh ph Vit Nam, th hin qua kt qu kinh t n tng trn nhiu lnh vc, to  vng vng cho tng trng cc nm tip theo.</p>\r\n<p>Hai Th tng nht tr thc y trin khai hiu qu cc tha thun cp cao, trong  c to thun li thc y thng mi u t, hp tc nng lng sch, gio dc o to, giao lu nhn dn; sm trao i v cc ni hm tin ti nng cp quan h Vit Nam v Singapore ln i tc Chin lc ton din vo thi gian ph hp.</p>\r\n<p>Hai Th tng cng nht tr sm c th ha quan h i tc Kinh t Xanh - Kinh t S  thit lp; m rng mng li cc khu cng nghip VSIP sang cc cc a phng xa trung tm ca Vit Nam, khuyn khch chuyn i cc khu VSIP truyn thng sang khu cng nghip kt hp nng lng (VSEP) thng minh, xanh, pht thi carbon thp</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 13, '2024-01-05 01:11:00', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:53:21', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:11:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"