(17, 89, 'Cu th c bit nht tuyn Vit Nam bo tin bun cho HLV Troussier st ngy hi qun', 'c-u-th-d-c-bi-t-nh-t-tuy-n-vi-t-nam-bao-tin-bu-n-cho-hlv-troussier-sat-ngay-h-i-quan', '<div class=\"detail__cnt-top\"><img src=\"images/7-1.png\" alt=\"\" />', '\r\n<h3 class=\"text detail-sapo\" data-role=\"sapo\" data-type=\"sapo\">Tin o Nguyn Thanh Nhn cho bit bn thn dnh chn thng v c th s rt lui khi i tuyn Vit Nam.</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"detail-cmain\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-content afcbc-body \" data-role=\"content\">\r\n<div class=\"detail-cover\">Hm 25/12, i tuyn Vit Nam  cng b danh sch 34 cu th  hng n Asian Cup 2023.</div>\r\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\r\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"Thanh Nhn dnh chn thng trc thi im ln tuyn Vit Nam.\" href=\"https://baogiaothong.mediacdn.vn/603483875699699712/2023/12/26/thanh-nhan-1703562583458849614624.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img id=\"img_663952401959886848\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"Cu th c bit nht tuyn Vit Nam bo tin bun cho HLV Troussier st ngy hi qun  - nh 1.\" src=\"https://baogiaothong.mediacdn.vn/603483875699699712/2023/12/26/thanh-nhan-1703562583458849614624.jpg\" alt=\"Cu th c bit nht tuyn Vit Nam bo tin bun cho HLV Troussier st ngy hi qun  - nh 1.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https://baogiaothong.mediacdn.vn/603483875699699712/2023/12/26/thanh-nhan-1703562583458849614624.jpg\" /></a></div>\r\n<figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\r\n<p class=\"\" data-placeholder=\"Nhp ch thch nh\">Thanh Nhn dnh chn thng trc thi im ln tuyn Vit Nam.</p>\r\n</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>Trong ln hi qun ny, bn cnh cc tr ct, HLV Troussier tip tc trao c hi cho dn cu th tr.</p>\r\n<p>Mt trong s nhng ci tn c nh cm qun ngi Php trao c hi chnh l tin o Nguyn Thanh Nhn.</p>\r\n<p>Nhng ng tic, ch sau t gi c gi ln tuyn, Thanh Nhn  xc nhn bn thn dnh chn thng v kh nng cao s rt lui.</p>\r\n<p>Ti gp chn thng c chn  trn u gia PVF  CAND vi Hu ti gii hng Nht quc gia.</p>\r\n<p>D kin phi mt 2-3 tun mi c th hi phc nn ti  thng bo cho cu lc b ch qun v pha i tuyn v tnh hnh chn thng  c phng n d phng, Thanh Nhn chia s.</p>\r\n<p>Thanh Nhn l cu th duy nht  gii hng Nht c HLV Troussier gi ln hi qun  hng n Asian Cup 2023.</p>\r\n<p>Cu th thuc bin ch PVF  CAND c nh gi rt tim nng khi anh s hu kh nng dt im n tng, xoay x tt.</p>\r\n<p>Vic Thanh Nhn dnh chn thng ngay trc thi im hi qun l tn tht ln ca tuyn Vit Nam.</p>\r\n<p>Nhng may mn, trong tay HLV Troussier lc ny ang c nhng ci tn rt cht lng lng nh Tun Hi, Vn Ton hay Tin Linh.</p>\r\n<p>ng ni, nhng ngi sao ny u ang dn ly li c phong  trong mu o CLB trc khi ln tuyn.</p>\r\n<p>Theo k hoch, ngy 31/12, tuyn Vit Nam s hi qun ti Trung tm o to bng  tr Vit Nam.</p>\r\n<p>Ti Asian Cup 2023, on qun o  ln lt ng  Nht Bn (14/1/2024), Indonesia (19/1) v Iraq (24/1).</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 13, '2024-01-05 01:11:18', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:54:15', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:11:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_posi