(18, 90, 'Tn hiu vui ca du lch Kin Giang', 'tin-hi-u-vui-c-a-du-l-ch-kien-giang', '<p><img src=\"images/dulich.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<h2 class=\"title-italic\">(KGO) - Cc hot ng du lch trn a bn Kin Giang  dn hi phc vi nhiu tn hiu tch cc. Ch tiu v lng khch, doanh thu  vt k hoch nm; ring du khch quc t vt n 63,8%.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"newscontent\">\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid\"><strong>QUC T NH GI CAO</strong></div>\r\n<p>Du lch Kin Giang tip tc c nhiu t chc du lch uy tn trn th gii xp hng cao  khu vc, chu  v th gii nh tp ch du lch Cond Nast Traveler (M) vinh danh Ph Quc nm trong top nhng hn o tuyt vi nht nm 2023; ring hng mc c s lu tr, Ph Quc c 5 i din c trao gii dn u khu vc ny.</p>\r\n<p>Trong khi , cng vin nc Aquatopia Water Park Ph Quc vt qua nhiu i th mnh t Trung Quc, Hn Quc, Singapore  nhn gii cng vin nc hng u chu  Tp ch du lch The Travel xp Ph Quc 3/17 hn o c chi ph du lch r nht th gii.</p>\r\n<p>Nhng thng cui nm 2023, Ph Quc lin tip n cc chuyn bay quc t a du khch n tham quan, ngh dng. y l lot tn hiu khi sc nh du s phc hi du lch t th trng khch quc t. Cc hng hng khng ln ca Hn Quc lin tip tng cng nhiu ng bay mi n Ph Quc. Cc hng thng tn ln ca x s kim chi cho rng Ph Quc l im n du lch m gia nh, bn b v cc cp i c th tn hng.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/images/2023/12/01/083446kgo_20231201_M%E1%BB%99t%20g%C3%B3c%20x%C3%A3%20%C4%91%E1%BA%A3o%20H%C3%B2n%20S%C6%A1n%20(Ki%C3%AAn%20H%E1%BA%A3i).webp\" alt=\"083446kgo_20231201_Mt gc x o Hn Sn (Kin Hi)\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>Mt gc x o Hn Sn, huyn Kin Hi.</em></p>\r\n<p>ng Yong Sung Ok - Trng Phng khu vc ng Nam  Cng ty du lch Hanatour (Hn Quc) nhn nh: Vit Nam, trong  c Ph Quc l im n c tm kim v ph bin nht vi du khch Hn Quc thi gian gn y do v tr a l gn nhau, c nhiu ng bay, gi v my bay r vi ngi Hn Quc. Ngoi ra, Vit Namcn hp dn du khch quc t bi chnh sch min hon ton th thc, thi hn tm tr 30 ngy.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_1\">\r\n<div id=\"ats-insert_ads-0-wrapper\" class=\"insert_ads insert_ads-2 show_advertisement rendered\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>ADVERTISEMENT</p>\r\n<div id=\"ats-insert_ads-0\" class=\"ats-slot\" data-google-query-id=\"CND_gpS0rIMDFcPxTAIdH6EGJA\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Gim c S Du lch Kin GiangBi Quc Thi cho bit vic khch quc t tr li Ph Quc ng mt phn t s nh gi khch quan cacc t chc, tp ch du lch uy tn hng u th gii v Ph Quc. Gn y nht, Travel Lemming (Hoa K) xp Ph Quc ng th 6 trong danh sch 50 im n du lch hng u th gii nm 2024. iu ny cho thy Ph Quc l im n c du khch a chung t v p,  cun ht v sn phm, cht lng dch v.</p>\r\n<p><strong>TO THM SC BT</strong></p>\r\n<p>Gn y, ti Hn Sn, huyn Kin Hi, du khch thch th n check in im du lch c kin trc kh c o - Flyup resort. y c xem l cng trnh gp phn lm thay i din mo du lch x hn khi thu ht lng ln du khch.</p>\r\n<p>ng Trn Hong Sn - du khch n t TP. Pleiku (Gia Lai) cho bit: Ti gh Hn Sn sau chuyn i Nam Du. Ti bt ng khi Hn Sn c u t mt c s lu tr rt p v khc bit. Hn Sn vn c li th v cnh quan, cn c ngun nhn lc du lch nhit tnh, hiu khch. Ti ngh ni ny ch cn gi gi cc dch v th thng hiu Hn Sn cn vn xa.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/images/2023/12/01/083433kgo_20231201_c%C3%A2u%20c%C3%A1%20gi%E1%BA%A3i%20tr%C3%AD%20tr%C3%AAn%20bi%E1%BB%83n%20R%E1%BA%A1ch%20V%E1%BA%B9m%20(TP.%20Ph%C3%BA%20Qu%E1%BB%91c).webp\" alt=\"083433kgo_20231201_cu c gii tr trn bin Rch Vm (TP\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>Khch du lch tham gia tour cu c gii tr trn bin Rch Vm (TP. Ph Quc).</em></p>\r\n<p>Theo Hip hi Du lch tnh Kin Giang, nm 2023 ngnh du lch chu nh hng nng ca suy thoi kinh t nhng cc hot ng du lch trn a bn Kin Giang dn hi phc vi nhiu tn hiu tch cc.Ch tiu v lng khch, doanh thu  vt k hoch nm; ring du khch quc t vt n 63,8%.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_2\"></div>\r\n<p>Theo ng Trn Quc Khnh - Ch tch Hip hi Du lch tnh,  gp phn thc y du lch phc hi, hip hi cnhiu chng trnh qung b, xc tin du lch Kin Giang n cc th trng du lch trong v ngoi nc. Hip hi ku gi cc thnh vin to sn phm du lch mi, nng cht lng sn phm du lch.</p>\r\n<p>Theo , ti Ph Quc, cc doanh nghip a vo khai thc nhiu sn phm du lch mi, ng cp nh Cu Hn, du thuyn 5 sao Nautilus v hng lot chng trnh kch cu du lch, chui l hi gii tr ng cp quc t thu ht lng ln du khch vui chi, khm ph.</p>\r\n<p>Theo S Du lch Kin Giang, ngnh du lch s phi hp n v lin quan, doanh nghip tng cng kch cu du lch; nghin cu,  xut chnh sch u i u t, to mi trng u t kinh doanh du lch thun li, thng thong cho doanh nghip.</p>\r\n<p>Song song , Kin Giang tp trung khai thc m hnh du lch kinh t v m qua cc hot ng biu din vn ha, ngh thut,m thc ti Ph Quc, Rch Gi, H Tin, Kin Hi</p>\r\n<p>Ring Ph Quc s pht trin thm cc nhm sn phm, dch v gn khm ph nt vn ha cng ng dn c  hai phng Dng ng v An Thi; nghin cu xy dng tuyn ph i b kt hp mua sm, m thc</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_3\"></div>\r\n<div>Tng lt du khch n Kin Giang nm 2023 c t 8.534.993 lt, tng 15,3% so cng k, vt 2,8% k hoch nm; trong  du khch quc t c n 573.272 lt, tng 203,3% so cng k nm 2022, vt 63,8% k hoch nm; tng doanh thu t du lch c t 17.479 t ng, tng 65,1% so cng k, vt 34,5% k hoch nm 2023.</div>\r\n</div>', 1, 15, '2024-01-05 01:11:53', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:54:25', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:11:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 5, 3, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 1, '*', '', ''),
(19, 91, 'Kin Hi n hn 450.320 lt khch du lch nm 2023', 'kien-h-i-don-hon-450-320-lu-t-khach-du-l-ch-nam-2023', '<p><img src=\"images/Cau_cang_Dao_cu_tron-quan_Dao_nam_du._xa_An_Sn,_Huyen_Kin_Hi,_tnh_Kin_Giang,_Vit_Nam,02-07-16-Dyt_-_panoramio.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<h2 class=\"title-italic\">(KGO) - Ngy 21-12, Huyn Kin Hi (Kin Giang) t chc hi ngh Ban Chp hnh ng b ln th 16 m rng tng kt tnh hnh thc hin nhim v, chnh tr nm 2023 v  ra phng hng nhim v nm 2024.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"newscontent\">\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid\"><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/images/2023/12/21/110102KGO%20-%20DSC_7075.webp\" alt=\"110102KGO - DSC_7075\" /></div>\r\n<p><em>Ph B th Thng trc Huyn y, Ch tch HND huyn Kin Hion Hng Duy (gia) trao gii cho cc c nhn t gii cuc thi vit bo v nn tng t tng ca ng nm 2023.</em></p>\r\n<p>Nm 2023, Ban Thng v Huyn y Kin Hi tp trung lnh o, ch o c 29/31 nhm ch tiu t Ngh quyt nm 2023, trong  21 ch tiu vt.</p>\r\n<p>ng b huyn pht trin 44 ng vin mi, t 110% k hoch. Cc chi, ng b trc thuc t chc kim tra, gim st 16 t chc ng vi 278 ng vin; thi hnh k lut 7 ng vin.</p>\r\n<p>Nm 2023, sn lng khai thc hi sn ca huyn ot hn 47.480 tn, t 97,62% k hoch; sn lng nui trng thy sn xut bn 1.197 tn, t 108,82% k hoch;n hn 450.320 lt khch du l, t 100,07% k hoch; doanh thu dch v lu tr v n ung c 582 t ng, t 96,20% k hoch.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/images/2023/12/21/110445KGO%20-%20DSC_6985.webp\" alt=\"110445KGO - DSC_6985\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>Ngidn x Hn Tre, huyn Kin Hi chm sc c lng b.</em></p>\r\n<p>Dp ny, Huyn Kin Hi khen thng 10 c nhn t gii cuc thi vit bo v nn tng t tng ca ng nm 2023.</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 15, '2024-01-05 01:12:15', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:54:38', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:12:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 4, 2, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 1, '*', '', '');
