(20, 92, 'Phi to im nhn cho du lch Kin Hi', 'ph-i-t-o-di-m-nh-n-cho-du-l-ch-kien-h-i', '<p><img src=\"images/images.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<h2 class=\"title-italic\">(KGO) - Gn y, du lch Kin Hi (Kin Giang) thu ht du khch bi v p hoang s. Tuy nhin,  gi chn khch lu hn, nhiu doanh nghip kinh doanh du lch cho rng Kin Hi cn c sn phm mi c o, trong  phi gi c gi dch v n nh.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"newscontent\">\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid\">Huyn Kin Hi nm pha ty nam ca T quc, gm 23 o. Cc o nh Hn Sn, Nam Du thu ht ng o du khch.</div>\r\n<p>Giai on 2021-2025, Kin Hi tch cc huy ng ngun lc  u t xy dng cc cng trnh trng im, nng cao cht lng kt cu h tng theo hng ng b nhm thu ht u t t cc thnh phn kinh t, pht trin kinh t bin, o, trong  c du lch.</p>\r\n<p>Kin Hi vn dng linh hot c ch, chnh sch u i cho nh u t; tng cng xc tin u t, khuyn khch t chc, c nhn thc hin d n u t, khai thc tim nng, li th ca a phng v du lch, nui trng thy sn gn du lch sinh thi quanh o v trn bin; xy dng Li Sn thnh khu du lch vn ha, sinh thi, ngh dng cht lng; qun o Nam Du thnh khu du lch khm ph, tri nghim, du lch ngh dng cht lng</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/images/2023/12/08/0934260917536028_KGO_DulichKienHai_bo%20bien.webp\" alt=\"0934260917536028_KGO_DulichKienHai_bo bien\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>Mt gc Hn Sn, huyn Kin Hi (Kin Giang).</em></p>\r\n<p>Cc doanh nghip kinh doanh hot ng du lch v du khch tng i du lch Kin Hi (Kin Giang) cho rng a phng c li th cnh ni rng hoang s, ngi dn thn thin v gi c bnh dn; trong  Hn Sn v Nam Du pht trin du lch mnh hn...</p>\r\n<p>ng L Minh Tm - Gim c Cng ty Long Xuyn Tourist An Giang cho bit: Chng ti khai thc nhiu t th trng Kin Giang, trong  c Hn Sn v Nam Du nhn c nhiu nh gi tt t du khch. Ngi dn Hn Sn, Nam Du lm du lch chim khong 60%; c xy ra tnh trng i phng khng ng vi phng khch t trc , chng trnh tour cha  v ng vi chng trnh cho bn. Theo ti ngi lm du lch cn gi gi bnh n, lm du lch chuyn nghip hn  khch du lch n nhiu ln.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_1\">\r\n<div id=\"ats-insert_ads-0-wrapper\" class=\"insert_ads insert_ads-2 show_advertisement rendered\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>ADVERTISEMENT</p>\r\n<div id=\"ats-insert_ads-0\" class=\"ats-slot\" data-google-query-id=\"CMf1yIG0rIMDFd0qewcdZBYIbw\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/images/2023/12/08/0918276028_KGO_DulichKienHai.webp\" alt=\"0918276028_KGO_DulichKienHai\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>Khch du lch tm bin ti x o Nam Du, huyn Kin Hi (Kin Giang).</em></p>\r\n<p>ng Trn Hong Sn - Gim c khch sn Vnh Hi, TP. Pleiku (Gia Lai) va c chuyn du lch ti Nam Du v Hn Sn. ng cho bit mnh n tng vi nhiu hot ng du lch nh tham quan lng b, cu c gii tr v thng thc m thc trn bin.</p>\r\n<p>ng Sn  n tham quan vn o gn 40 nm tui,dng th sn phm OCOP ru o Hn Sn; tham quan vn nhn c th trn 100 nm tui; chinh phc  cao ca nh ng Rng, nh Ma Thin Lnh vchim ngng v p ca bi Cy Mn, bi Cy Da Nm</p>\r\n<p>Theo ng Sn, li th ca Nam Du, Hn Sn l thin nhin hoang s, ngi dn thn thin, m thc hp dn, nhiu c s lu tr u t mi, p Ngoi ra qu lu nim bn ti ch, cc lng chi do ngi dn a phng t lm nn gi phi chng.</p>\r\n<p>\"Tuy nhin,  du lch pht trin bn vng, a phng tn dng ngun nhn lc pht trin du lch nhit tnh, hiu khch v gii thiu n du khch nt p, vn ha, vng t v ngi dn x o Kin Hi bng nhng cu chuyn ca a phng, ng Trn Hong Snchia s.</p>\r\n<p>ng Mai Tun Kit - Gim c Cng ty C phn Dch v Thng mi v Du lch Ph Cng, TP. Rch Gi (Kin Giang)nhn nh sn phm du lch  Hn Sn, Nam Du ging nhau. Du khch n y n hi sn, ln ngm san h, chy xe quanh o khm ph i sng ngi dn x o, sau  v phng ngh v kt thc chuyn i chi. a phng cn c cc im nhn nh con ng hoa, cung ng tnh yu hay t chc chng trnh, s kin vui chi trn bi bin</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_2\"></div>\r\n<table cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" align=\"right\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Ph Ch tch UBND huyn Kin Hi L Minh Tr,cho bit: \"Thi gian ti Kin Hi phi hp cc n v lin quan tip tc nng cht lng dch v du lch, x l rc thi, to sn phm mi hp dn; tng cng qun l nh nc v du lch, thc y du lch a phng pht trin tt hn.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Cc doanh nghip kinh doanh du lch u cho rng, Kin Hi cn tng cng lin kt, hp tc pht trin du lch, xy dng cc tour, tuyn du lch ng bin kt ni ni b, khu vc v lin vng, ng thi a dng ha v nng cao cht lng sn phm du lch...</p>\r\n<p>\"Kin Hi cn tng cng qung b, thu ht thm cc d n u t, a dng loi hnh du lch, tp trung cho loi hnhdu lch sinh thi, du lch bin ngm rn san h, du lch lng ngh, du lch cng ng homestay, du lch gn l hi, tn ngng dn gian... Tm li, cn phi to im nhn cho du lch Kin Hi\", ng Mai Tun Kit ni.</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 15, '2024-01-05 01:12:36', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:54:52', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:12:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 4, 1, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"