(21, 93, '[nh] Bnh xo  l hi Nguyn Trung Trc', 'nh-banh-xeo-l-h-i-nguy-n-trung-tr-c', '<p><img src=\"images/KGO_20231010_BANHXEO6.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<h2 class=\"title-italic\">(KGO) - Theo quan nim ca ngi min Ty, bnh xo l mn n thay cm; mang tinh thn hi t, sum vy thng c ch bin, thng thc trong nhng ngy l, tt.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"newscontent\">\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid\"><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/image/2023/10/10/KGO_20231010_BANHXEO6.jpg\" alt=\"KGO_20231010_BANHXEO6\" /></div>\r\n<p><em>Bnh xo phc v min ph ti L hi Nguyn Trung Trc.</em></p>\r\n<p>Xut pht t tinh thn , nhiu nm qua ng Phan Vn Thi, ch tri bnh xo Tm Thi (An Giang) lun n Rch Gi (Kin Giang) dp l hi Nguyn Trung Trc phc v bnh xo min ph cho khch thp phng.</p>\r\n<p>ng Thi cho bit: Nm nay chng ti chun b khong 2 tn go, vi tn rau, c qu v tu h  phc v bnh xo min ph cho b con v d l hi ng Nguyn. Chng ti hy vng gp phn cng ban t chc l hi phc v tt hn cho b con.y cng l cch  nhng ngi con nh chng ti by t lng bit n, lng thnh knh vi c Nguyn.</p>\r\n<p>Ni v vic lm bnh xo, dn gian cng c cu v vui: Ngi no xu xu xay bt, lt hnh; ngi no lanh lanh bm nhn,  bnh. Ng  vic lm bnh xo, n bnh xo c ng ngi mi vui hn l ni v nhan sc hay tnh cch. </p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/image/2023/10/10/KGO_20231010_BANHXEO1.jpg\" alt=\"KGO_20231010_BANHXEO1\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>Lng bnh phc v khch rt ln nn cc cng on nh p nc ct, trn bt pho thchin bng my. </em></p>\r\n<p>Ti L hi Nguyn Trung Trc, nhiu nhm ngi chia thnh nhiu t pha bt, lt rau, ct c,  bnh... Mi ngi mt vic nhng hvn ni ci rm r, gp thm cho bukhng khl hivui ti,m m.</p>\r\n<p>i tay thon thot, b H Th Lan, ng Th x Tn Chu(An Giang) ph trch bnh bn10 ci cho khin nhiu ngi khng khi thn phc. Tay mc bt ri u vo chic cho ang nng v nghing cho nhanh  vnh xo c ng u khi thnh phm...</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_1\">\r\n<div id=\"ats-insert_ads-0-wrapper\" class=\"insert_ads insert_ads-2 show_advertisement rendered\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>ADVERTISEMENT</p>\r\n<div id=\"ats-insert_ads-0\" class=\"ats-slot\" data-google-query-id=\"CIuHq9e1rIMDFc_VTAIdxWwFRw\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>B Lan cho bit: Ti tham gia l gi c Nguyn hn 20 nm qua, c kinh nghim nn ti c giao  bnh. Bp cng hn 10 ngi  bnh, mi ln ra bnh lin tc khong 100 bnh nhng khng  phc v khch thp phng.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/image/2023/10/10/KGO_20231010_BANHXEO9.jpg\" alt=\"KGO_20231010_BANHXEO9\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>Nhiu my chy ht cng sut  kp nguyn liu lm bnh.</em></p>\r\n<p>Bnh c  lin tc, khch thp phng ch cn xp hng vng quanh u bp s lybnh vo da cho tng ngi. Sau khi nhn bnh, khch thp phng di chuyn v ch ngi  thng thc hoc em v nh</p>\r\n<p>Ti t ng Thp v ving ng Nguyn sng nay. Sau khi thp nhang tng nh ng, ti c mi ngi r i n bnh xo. Bnh xo  y rt ngon, v bnh gin vn gi c  bo, nhn th m ..., b H Th Tuyn chia s.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/image/2023/10/10/KGO_20231010_BANHXEO8.jpg\" alt=\"KGO_20231010_BANHXEO8\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>Nhn bnh c lm hon ton t rau, c ti.</em></p>\r\n<p><em><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/image/2023/10/10/KGO_20231010_BANHXEO5.jpg\" alt=\"KGO_20231010_BANHXEO5\" /></em></p>\r\n<p><em>Ch L Tuyn, ng TP Rch Gi c thi gian 5 nm tham gia  bnh xo phc v khch thp phng.</em></p>\r\n<p><em><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/image/2023/10/10/KGO_20231010_BANHXEO4.jpg\" alt=\"KGO_20231010_BANHXEO4\" /></em></p>\r\n<p><i>Cn cnh chic bnh xo chay ti L hi Nguyn Trung Trc.</i></p>\r\n<p><i><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/image/2023/10/10/KGO_20231010_BANHXEO7.jpg\" alt=\"KGO_20231010_BANHXEO7\" /></i></p>\r\n<p><i>Khng ch min ph bnh xo, khch thp phng cn c nhng ngi lm cng qu phc v bnh n tn bn n.</i></p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_2\"></div>\r\n<p><i><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/image/2023/10/10/KGO_20231010_BANHXEO2.jpg\" alt=\"KGO_20231010_BANHXEO2\" /></i></p>\r\n<p><em>Khch thpphng vui v thng thc bnh xo chay tiL hi Nguyn Trung Trc.</em></p>\r\n</div>', 1, 16, '2024-01-05 01:13:08', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:55:02', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:13:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 4, 1, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 1, '*', '', ''),
(22, 94, 'Thm ngon mn tm kh x Lnh Hunh', 'thom-ngon-mon-tom-kho-x-linh-huynh', '<p><img src=\"images/hnh 1 (18).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<h2 class=\"title-italic\">(KGO) - Tm kh x  x Lnh Hunh, huyn Hn t (Kin Giang) c hng v c trng, d ch bin v kt hp vi nhiu mn n khc nhau. y cn l mn qu c nhiu ngi la chn khi c dp gh thm huyn Hn t.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"newscontent\">\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid\">V chng anh Nguyn Vn m v ch Hunh D c bit n l ngi u tin lm mn tm kh x  x Lnh Hunh, n nay anh ch c hn 5 nm lm tm kh x.</div>\r\n<p>Ch D cho bit: Mt ln v thm qu chng  tnh Bc Liu ngay v thu hoch tm, ti tr ti lm mn n t tm mi gia nh. Nu luc, nu lu hoc nng th qu quen thuc nn ti th lm kh. Sau khi thng thc, gia nh ai cng khen tm vn gi c hng v c trng. Ti mang mt t v lm qu cho hng xm v tm kh bo qun c lu hn.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/image/2023/10/25/h%C3%ACnh%201%20(18).jpg\" alt=\"h%C3%ACnh%201%20(18)\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>Ch Hunh D x tm s  lm tm kh x.</em></p>\r\n<p>Sau khi nhn phn hi tch cc t mi ngi, anh m bn vi ch D lm thm tm kh  bn th. Ban uanh ch khng lm nhiu m ch mua hn chc k tm s, kt qu mang li rt kh quan, tm kh x nhanh chng ht hng, nhiu khch cn t thm t 2-3kg.</p>\r\n<p>Lc y vo dp tt nn khch t hng rt nhiu, c hm ti v v lt tm t 2 gi sng n tn 14 gi  kp mang tm phi ri giao cho khch hng. Gia nh ti nm  bn c khong 500kg tm, t  ti duy tr lm tm kh  bn c nm ch khng ch bn vo nhng ngy tt, anh m k.</p>\r\n<p>Tm kh x ca gia nh anh m khng tm p nhiu gia v, sau khi lt v, x thn tm lm i theo chiu dc th p mt cht nc mm ri em phi nng. Thi gian phi tm tt nht l t 7 gi n 14 gi, nng cng gt th tm cng ngon.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_1\">\r\n<div id=\"ats-insert_ads-0-wrapper\" class=\"insert_ads insert_ads-2 show_advertisement rendered\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>ADVERTISEMENT</p>\r\n<div id=\"ats-insert_ads-0\" class=\"ats-slot\" data-google-query-id=\"CNuRs8e1rIMDFVEaewcdC4YE5g\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>Khi lm tm kh x, cng on kh khn nht l lt v v x tm v phi ngi lin tc, tay ngm nc trong nhiu gi d l lot. Ngi lt v, x tm phi tht kho lo nu khng tm s mt tht, ht k, v l do ny nn anh m v gia nh thng t tay lm tm, khi no s lng khch t hn 70kg mi thu nhn cng  ph vic.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/image/2023/10/25/Tom%202.jpg\" alt=\"Tom%202\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>Tm s sau khi c phi kh.</em></p>\r\n<p>V chng anh m chn tm s ti  lm tm kh x, thnh phm c gi 1,1 triu ng/kg. Gii thch cho vic khng chn loi tm c gi r hn tm s  lm kh, ch D ni: Ti th dng tm th bin lm kh  gim gi bn nhng tht bi. Tht tm th bin sau khi lm kh s b b, khng c mi thm, n trong ngy ch khng  c lu v d hng. La tm kh  ti phi b i, l hn 15 triu ng. Ti nhn ra tm s gi cao nhng cht lng tt, khch hng rt ng  nn ti ch lm kh bng tm s ch khng s dng bt c loi tm no khc.</p>\r\n<p>Anh Nguyn Khnh Hng, ng qun 3 (TP. H Ch Minh) l khch hng mua tm kh quen thuc ca gia nh anh m. Anh Hng cho bit: Dng qua tm kh x  nhiu ni khc nhng ti ng  nht tm kh x ca gia nh anh m. Anh ch khng s dng phm mu, cht bo qun hoc tm p cc loi gia v nn tm kh c v t nhin, tht tm dai, ngt v m , d l tm kh nhng vn cm nhn c  ti. Ti v gia nh thng chin hoc nng tm kh  n cng vi cm, m hoc n khng cng rt ngon. Tt ny ti tip tc t hng  mang biu bn b, ng nghip.</p>\r\n<p>Hng nm t thng 11 dng lch n Tt Nguyn n l khong thi gian gia nh anh m nhn c nhiu n t hng tm kh x nht, v vy nn t gia thng 10, gia nh anh m tm ngun mua tm  nhng tri tm trong v ngoi tnh. Ch D lin h khch hng s, l thn quen  trong tnh, cc tnh An Giang, Bnh Dng, ng Nai  tng hp n hng.</p>\r\n<p>C th ni ngh lm tm kh x khng phi cng vic chnh ca gia nh anh m nhng li gip gia nh anh tng thu nhp v n nh cuc sng.</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 16, '2024-01-05 01:13:30', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:55:15', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:13:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 4, 0, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 1, '*', '', ''),
(23, 95, 'Th tng Singapore: Vit Nam t kt qu kinh t n tng', 'th-tu-ng-singapore-vi-t-nam-d-t-k-t-qu-kinh-t-n-tu-ng', '<p><img src=\"images/NQH_0592.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<h2 class=\"title-italic\">(KGO) - Sng 18-12, ti Tokyo, Nht Bn, Th tng Phm Minh Chnh  gp Th tng Singapore L Hin Long nhn dp tham d Hi ngh thng nh u tin v \"Cng ng pht thi rng bng 0 chu  (AZEC)\".</h2>\r\n<div class=\"newscontent\">\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/images/2023/12/18/165951ttg-viet-sing-1702886402996229441956.webp\" alt=\"165951ttg-viet-sing-1702886402996229441956\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>Th tng Phm Minh Chnh n Th tng Singapore L Hin Long thm chnh thc Vit Nam t ngy 27 n 29-8-2023</em>.</p>\r\n<p>Hai Th tng cng by t hi lng v mt nm 2023 si ni cc hot ng thit thc k nim 50 nm thit lp quan h ngoi giao, 10 nm thit lp quan h i tc Chin lc, c bit l cc chuyn thm v trao i cp cao.</p>\r\n<p>Th tng L Hin Long cng nh gi cao chnh sch i ngoi v iu hnh kinh t ca Chnh ph Vit Nam, th hin qua kt qu kinh t n tng trn nhiu lnh vc, to  vng vng cho tng trng cc nm tip theo.</p>\r\n<p>Hai Th tng nht tr thc y trin khai hiu qu cc tha thun cp cao, trong  c to thun li thc y thng mi u t, hp tc nng lng sch, gio dc o to, giao lu nhn dn; sm trao i v cc ni hm tin ti nng cp quan h Vit Nam v Singapore ln i tc Chin lc ton din vo thi gian ph hp.</p>\r\n<p>Hai Th tng cng nht tr sm c th ha quan h i tc Kinh t Xanh - Kinh t S  thit lp; m rng mng li cc khu cng nghip VSIP sang cc cc a phng xa trung tm ca Vit Nam, khuyn khch chuyn i cc khu VSIP truyn thng sang khu cng nghip kt hp nng lng (VSEP) thng minh, xanh, pht thi carbon thp</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 18, '2024-01-05 01:14:11', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:55:27', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:14:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 6, 1, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 1, '*', '', ''),
(24, 96, 'Kin Giang y mnh thc hin cc gii php thu ht du khch', 'kien-giang-d-y-m-nh-th-c-hi-n-cac-gi-i-phap-thu-hut-du-khach', '<p><img src=\"images/hoinghi2.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<h2 class=\"title-italic\">(KGO) - Trong chuyn mc Dn hi - Chnh quyn tr li k ny, Gim c S Du lch tnh Kin Giang Bi Quc Thi tr li cc cu hi xung quanh ch  Kin Giang tng cng, y mnh cc gii php thu ht khch du lch.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"newscontent\">\r\n<p>-<strong>Phng vin</strong>: Sp n tt dng lch v Tt Nguyn n Gip Thn nm 2024, hin ngnh du lch Kin Giang c k hoch cng nh chng trnh c bit g  thu ht du khch n Kin Giang?</p>\r\n<p>-<strong>ng ch Bi Quc Thi</strong>:Ngnh du lch ch o cc hip hi du lch, hip hi u bp v cc doanh nghip du lch t chc cc hot ng, s kin gn vi tt dng lch dnh cho du khch, nht l khch quc t n Kin Giang tham quan, du lch kt hp vui chi v n nm mi. S c chui cc s kin c sc din ra ti TP. Ph Quc nh chng trnh i nhc hi quc t 8Wonder Winter Festival; trnh din, gii tr, pho hoa gn vi s kin Countdown n mng nm mi phc v du khch v ngi dn.</p>\r\n<p>TP. H Tin t chc s kin l hi Tao n Chiu Anh Cc. Huyn Hn t t chc cc hot ng k nim ngy hy sinh Anh hng lc lng v trang nhn dn Phan Th RngKin Giang s t chc cc hot ng, s kin, chng trnh ngh thut gn vi l hi pho hoa n giao tha dp Tt Nguyn n Gip Thn ti TP. Rch Gi v cc a phng vng du lch trng im. y s l im nhn c bit  phc v ngi dn v du khch.</p>\r\n<p>-<strong>Phng vin:</strong>Ngnh du lch Kin Giang t ra mc tiu v gii php g cho nm 2024?</p>\r\n<p>-<strong>ng ch Bi Quc Thi</strong>: Nm 2024, ngnh du lch tnh t mc tiu n 9,2 triu lt khch n tham quan, du lch; trong  c 680.000 lt khch quc t, tng thu t du lch t 20.000 t ng.  t c cc ch tiu  ra, ngnh du lch cng cc ngnh, cc cp, a phng v cng ng doanh nghip trin khai ng b nhiu nhim v, gii php; trong  tp trung vo cc ni dung ch yu nh sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_1\"></div>\r\n<p>Mt l, xy dng sn phm, dch v hp dn du khch: Khuyn khch, ku gi cng ng doanh nghip, t chc, c nhn kinh doanh dch v du lch cng c, lm mi cc loi hnh, sn phm, dch v du lch hin c. Nghin cu xy dng cc sn phm dch v mi a dng, c o trn c s tim nng, li th, gn vi pht huy gi tr di sn v bn sc vn ha dn tc nh du lch ngh dng bin, o, du lch vn ha, lch s, du lch sinh thi, du lch nng nghip, nng thn, du lch MICE, du lch golf, du lch m ci</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/images/2023/12/25/092246_LTH2488%20(1).webp\" alt=\"092246_LTH2488 (1)\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>Gim c S Du lch tnh Kin Giang Bi Quc Thi (bn tri) trao i vi phng vin Bo Kin Giang.</em></p>\r\n<p>Hai l, truyn thng, xc tin qung b du lch: Tng cng truyn thng, xc tin qung b du lch, i mi phng thc, cng c, ng dng cng ngh s trong xc tin du lch; t chc xc tin c trng tm, trng im, ph hp nh hng pht trin sn phm, thng hiu du lch trn c s kt qu nghin cu, d bo. Xc nh li th trng ngun, th trng mc tiu, th trng tim nng trong v ngoi nc  tp trung xc tin, qung b c trng tm, trng im.</p>\r\n<p>Ba l, v lin kt vng: Tip tc trin khai cc chng trnh lin kt, hp tc pht trin du lch vi cc a phng cm pha ty khu vc ng bng sng Cu Long vi vai tr cm trng, chng trnh lin kt gia 13 tnh, thnh ph ng bng sng Cu Long vi TP. H Ch Minh. Xem xt lin kt, hp tc vi cc tnh, thnh ph khu vc Ty Bc, min Trung, Ty Nguyn v c lin kt hp tc  nc ngoi.</p>\r\n<p>Bn l, o to, bi dng ngun nhn lc du lch: T chc cc kha o to, bi dng v chuyn mn, nghip v cho ngi lao ng trc tip phc v khch du lch p ng yu cu ngy cng cao ca du khch trong tnh hnh mi v hi nhp quc t. T chc iu tra, phn loi trnh  nghip v ca ngi lao ng hin ang lm vic trong ngnh du lch. Tranh th s tham gia ca cc chuyn gia t vn v nhn s cp cao trong hot ng o to thng qua vic  ngh t vn, mi gp  cho cc ni dung chng trnh o to, tp hun, bi dng chuyn mn, nghip v. H tr cc doanh nghip, c s o to trong vic o to pht trin ngun nhn lc du lch, t chc o to, bi dng kin thc cho cng ng tham gia phc v du lch.</p>\r\n<p>Nm l, v quy hoch: Tip tc hon thin quy hoch chi tit v u t h tng phc v pht trin du lch, c bit ti cc vng du lch trng im. Tp trung huy ng ngun vn u t kt cu h tng ng b, tng bc hin i cho 4 vng du lch trng im ca tnh, ch trng h tng v giao thng, vn ti c ng b, ng bin v ng hng khng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_2\"></div>\r\n<p>Su l, ch tr, phi hp vi cc n v c lin quan tham mu UBNDtnh xy dng v trnh Th tng Chnh ph ph duyt  n pht trin TP. Ph Quc thnh trung tm dch v du lch sinh thi cht lng cao, du lch bin o tm c quc gia v quc t.</p>\r\n<p>By l, qun l nh nc v du lch: Tng cng cng tc qun l nh nc v du lch, bo m an ninh, an ton cho du khch, to mi trng u t kinh doanh du lch thun li, thng thong cho cc nh u t v cc doanh nghip du lch hot ng kinh doanh. Phi hp vi cc c quan, n v lin quan ci tin mnh m quy trnh kim sot th tc xut, nhp cnh, to iu kin thun li nht cho khch du lch quc t n tham quan, du lch. m bo v sinh mi trng, v sinh, an ton thc phm, v sinh, an ton phng dch trn a bn qun l. Qun l cht ch v gi c dch v du lch, yu cu cc n v kinh doanh dch v phi nim yt gi.</p>\r\n<p>-<strong>Phng vin</strong>: Ring i vi Ph Quc l khu du lch trng im ca tnh, trong thi gian ti s c nhng sn phm du lch g ni bt hoc c chnh sch g  kch cu a du lch Ph Quc pht trin mnh?</p>\r\n<p>-<strong>ng ch Bi Quc Thi</strong>: i vi Ph Quc, ngnh du lch  phi hp vi UBND TP. Ph Quc, Hi u t pht trin du lch Ph Quc v cng ng doanh nghip ti Ph Quc tp trung trin khai nhiu nhim v, gii php vi chui cc hot ng, s kin thu ht khch du lch.</p>\r\n<p>T nay n Tt Nguyn n Gip Thn, Ph Quc s tp trung t chc cc hot ng, s kin sau: Chui hot ng truyn thng v xc tin qung b du lch Ph Quc vi thng ip Ti yu Ph Quc - I L.O.V.E Phu Quoc. Truyn thng v ma vng Ph Quc nhm qung b v p ca thin nhin, thu ht du khch n tri nghim trong ma p nht nm trn cc phng tin truyn thng, bo ch trong nc v quc t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_3\"></div>\r\n<p>T chc Ngy Ph Quc lan ta n cc th trng trng im trong nc nh cc thnh ph H Ni,  Nng, thnh ph H Ch Minh; t chc hi ch ch  gp g cc i l du lch, KOL, trin lm, tri ngh thut...</p>\r\n<p>Xy dng website www.visitPhuQuoc.com.vn kt ni vi cc trang thng tin in t, cc knh truyn thng chnh thng ca Kin Giang.<br />Gi tin nhn Zalo/sms cho mng khi du khch n vi Ph Quc. Kt ni n landing page www.visitPhuQuoc.com.vn  khch truy cp, ly thng tin tra cu tri nghim khi ti vi Ph Quc.</p>\r\n<p>Xy dng v trin khai h thng nhn din chung chin dch Ti yu Ph Quc - I L.O.V.E Phu Quoc trn ton thnh ph.<br />Qung b b nhn din ring ca cc chng trnh kinh doanh, marketing ca doanh nghip.</p>\r\n<p>Truyn thng quc t v im n Ph Quc. Qung b v p, tri nghim Ph Quc trn phng tin truyn thng vi th trng trng im Hn Quc, Thi Lan, n  v mt s nc khc. T chc n on TikToker quc t, t chc on fesstrip cho phng vin quc t thng tr ti Vit Nam.</p>\r\n<p>Countdown 2024 n nm mi.</p>\r\n<p>T chc i nhc hi quc t 8Wonder Winter Festival vi s gp mt ca mt trong nhng ban nhc c yu thch nht th k 21 - Maroon 5.</p>\r\n<p>T chc s kin nh k Ngy xanh Ph Quc.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid_4\"></div>\r\n<p>Ngnh du lch s tng cng cng tc qun l nh nc v du lch; trong  tp trung tuyn truyn, ph bin php lut v kinh doanh du lch v cc quy nh ca php lut khc c lin quan n hot ng du lch  cc t chc, c nhn tham gia hot ng du lch. Cng c, kin ton t kim tra lin ngnh gim st, kim sot cht lng v gi c dch v du lch Ph Quc.</p>\r\n<p>i vi cc nhim v lu di, Ph Quc s cng vi cc a phng thc hin theo cc gii php chung nh  trao i  t c mc tiu chung ca tnh.</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 18, '2024-01-05 01:14:31', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:55:38', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:14:31', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 5, 0, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 1, '*', '', ''),
(25, 97, 'Kin Giang phc hi, n nh v pht trin kinh t - x hi', 'kien-giang-ph-c-h-i-n-d-nh-va-phat-tri-n-kinh-t-xa-h-i', '<p><img src=\"images/phatbieu.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>(PLVN) - Nm 2023, tnh Kin Giang c quy m tng sn phm trn a bn (GRDP) c t 73.377 t ng, vt 0,68% k hoch, tc  tng trng 6,79%.Ngy 25/12, HND tnh Kin Giang kho X, nhim k 2021 - 2026, khai mc k hp 20 (k hp cui nm 2023) tng kt tnh hnh ngh quyt ca HND tnh v nhim v pht trin kinh t - x hi nm 2023 v xem xt gii quyt mt s ni dung thuc thm quyn.</p>\r\n<div class=\"article__body cms-body \">\r\n<table class=\"picture\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"pic\"><img class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" title=\"ng Mai Vn Hunh - Ph b th Tnh u Kin Giang, Ch tch HND tnh Kin Giang - pht biu khai mc k hp 20 (k hp cui nm) ca HND tnh Kin Giang kho X, nhim k 2021-2026 (nh: Khnh Thu)\" src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/zshvwyvobvhvim/2023_12_25/1mvhuynh-6223.jpg\" alt=\"ng Mai Vn Hunh - Ph b th Tnh u Kin Giang, Ch tch HND tnh Kin Giang - pht biu khai mc k hp 20 (k hp cui nm) ca HND tnh Kin Giang kho X, nhim k 2021-2026 (nh: Khnh Thu)\" width=\"840\" height=\"560\" data-height=\"1707\" data-image-id=\"947668\" data-src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/zshvwyvobvhvim/2023_12_25/1mvhuynh-6223.jpg\" data-width=\"2560\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"caption\">\r\n<p>ng Mai Vn Hunh - Ph b th Tnh u Kin Giang, Ch tch HND tnh Kin Giang - pht biu khai mc k hp 20 (k hp cui nm) ca HND tnh Kin Giang kho X, nhim k 2021-2026 (nh: Khnh Thu)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>ng Nguyn Thanh Nhn - Ph Ch tch UBND tnh Kin Giang - cho bit: Nm 2023, tnh Kin Giang c quy m tng sn phm trn a bn tnh (GRDP) c t 73.377 t ng, vt 0,68% k hoch, tc  tng trng 6,79% (k hoch 6,5%).</p>\r\n<div class=\"ads_middle\"></div>\r\n<p>Nng - lm - thy sn  a phng tng 2,96%; cng nghip - xy dng, tng 8,36%; thng mi - dch v, tng 10,02%; thu sn phm tr tr cp sn phm, tng 5,95%; cng nghip - xy dng, chim 20,53%<em>;</em>dch v chim 37,53% v thu nhp khu, thu sn phm tr tr cp sn phm chim 4,92%<em>.</em>GRDP bnh qun u ngi  a phng c t 73,74 triu ng, tng 3,85% k hoch.</p>\r\n<p>c bit, nm 2023, tnh Kin Giang c n trn 8,5 triu lt khch, vt 2,8% k hoch, tng 15% so cng k. Ring khch du lch quc t t 573.000 lt, vt 63,8% k hoch, tng doanh thu du lch gn 17.500 t ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ads_middle\"></div>\r\n<table class=\"picture\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"pic\"><img class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" title=\"ng Nguyn Thanh Nhn - Ph Ch tch UBND tnh Kin Giang - cho bit nm 2023, Kin Giang phc hi v pht trin kinh t mnh m. (nh: Khnh Thu)\" src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/zshvwyvobvhvim/2023_12_25/1ngthanhnhan-3602.jpg\" alt=\"ng Nguyn Thanh Nhn - Ph Ch tch UBND tnh Kin Giang - cho bit nm 2023, Kin Giang phc hi v pht trin kinh t mnh m. (nh: Khnh Thu)\" width=\"840\" height=\"647\" data-height=\"987\" data-image-id=\"947669\" data-src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/zshvwyvobvhvim/2023_12_25/1ngthanhnhan-3602.jpg\" data-width=\"1280\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"caption\">\r\n<p>ng Nguyn Thanh Nhn - Ph Ch tch UBND tnh Kin Giang - cho bit nm 2023, Kin Giang phc hi v pht trin kinh t mnh m. (nh: Khnh Thu)</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>ng Nhn cho bit thm: Kinh t tuy c phc hi v tng trng kh; c cu kinh t chuyn dch ng hng, nhng cn chm. Do ,  pht trin kinh t x hi trong nm 2024, a phng tip tc tp trung thc hin cc chnh sch gp phn kim sot lm pht, n nh nn kinh t; y mnh gii ngn vn u t cng, to nn tng cho pht trin nhanh v bn vng. Bn cnh , tnh Kin Giang thc hin ng b, hiu qu cng tc ci cch hnh chnh, ci thin mi trng kinh doanh. To iu kin pht trin cc thnh phn kinh t, nng cao nng lc cnh tranh trn a bn tnh.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, tnh Kin Giang phn u s dng hiu qu ngun nhn lc, nht l ngun nhn lc cht lng cao, gn vi y mnh i mi sng to, ng dng v pht trin mnh m khoa hc, cng ngh. Ch ng ng ph hiu qu vi bin i kh hu, phng, chng thin tai, pht trin sn xut, n nh cuc sng ngi dn, ng Nhn ni.</p>\r\n<div class=\"article__author\"></div>\r\n</div>', 1, 17, '2024-01-05 01:14:59', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:55:51', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:14:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 4, 1, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 1, '*', '', ''),
(26, 98, 'Ngnh Cng an v Gio dc o to tnh Kin Giang tch cc thc hin chuyn i s', 'nganh-cong-an-va-giao-d-c-dao-t-o-t-nh-kien-giang-tich-c-c-th-c-hi-n-chuy-n-d-i-s', '<p><img src=\"images/nganhcongan.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>(PLVN) -Qua thi gianthc hin hiu qu chuyn i s, xy dng chnh quyn s, Chnh ph in t, n nayCng an tnh cng nhS Gio dc v o to tnh Kin Giang  y mnh ng dng cng ngh thng tin trong hot ng chuyn mn. Qua ,gp phn nng cao cht lng phc v ngi dn, doanh nghip cng nh cht lng qun l, ging dy v hc tp...</p>\r\n<div class=\"article__body cms-body \">\r\n<p>i t Nguyn Nht Trng, Ph Gim c Cng an tnh Kin Giang cho bit: Thc hin chuyn i s nhm nng cao cht lng, hiu qu phc v ngi dn v doanh nghip; nng cao hiu qu phng, chng tham nhng vt v phng, chng ti phm. Cng an tnh Kin Giang  thc hin 124 th tc hnh chnh dch v cng trc tuyn trn Cng dch v cng ca B Cng an, gip ngi dn gim thi gian i li, ch i, chun b v np cc giy t; tip nhn, gii quyt h s, th tc hnh chnh t gn 79%. Ring  n 06 ca Chnh ph, ngnh  thc hin dch v cng trc tuyn i vi 11 th tc hnh chnh.</p>\r\n<table class=\"picture\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"pic\"><img class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" title=\"i t Nguyn Nht Trng - Ph Gim c Cng an Kin Giang pht biu.\" src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/zshvwyvobvhvim/2023_12_25/cds1-9867.jpg\" alt=\"i t Nguyn Nht Trng - Ph Gim c Cng an Kin Giang pht biu.\" width=\"840\" height=\"538\" data-height=\"1313\" data-image-id=\"947631\" data-src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/zshvwyvobvhvim/2023_12_25/cds1-9867.jpg\" data-width=\"2048\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"caption\">\r\n<p>i t Nguyn Nht Trng - Ph Gim c Cng an Kin Giang pht biu.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>n v huy ng lc lng thu thp, cp nht, chnh sa thng tin dn c. n nay, ngnh c ngun d liu cng dn trn 2,1 triu khu v c duy tr m bo d liu lun ng, , sch, sng\". Tnh n ngy 19/6/2023, tnh Kin Gianh hon thnh 100% ch tiu cp Cn cc cng dn gn chp in t cho cng dn  iu kin; thu nhn, kch hot ti khon nh danh in t t 100%. T , to ra cng c  ngi dn thc hin cc giao dch trn mi trng in t m bo chnh xc, nhanh chng, tit kim.</p>\r\n<p>Ngnh cn y mnh thc hin tip nhn, gii quyt h s th tc hnh chnh v thanh ton ph, l ph cho t chc c nhn, doanh nghip qua dch v cng trc tuyn. Qua , mang li hiu qu tch cc, gip gim chi ph v thi gian cho nhn dn. Gp phn nng cao Ch s ci cch hnh chnh ca Cng an tnh (c nng hng t loi Kh ln Tt so vi 63 tnh, thnh ph trn ton quc).</p>\r\n<div class=\"ads_middle\"></div>\r\n<p>Cng vi , cng an tnh Kin Giang cng  h tr S Ni v lp, thm nh h s  n sp xp n v hnh chnh cp huyn, cp x vi trn 2 triu cng dn ti 144 n v hnh chnh cp x. Ngnh cng an  cung cp thng tin v c tr phc v kim tra, xc nhn v u tin vng cho 13.600 th sinh tham d K thi Tt nghip Trung hc C s, Trung hc Ph thng v xt tuyn i hc, Cao ng nm 2023; Phng nga cc hnh vi li dng lch s c tr  xc nhn im u tin vng. ng thi, Cng an tnh Kin Giang  \"lm sch\" 12.000 d liu thng tin thu bao, hn ch tnh trng sim rc\", ti phm la o, e da, vu khng; xc thc nh danh c nhn, Cn cc cng dn vi ngi tham gia bo him x hi, bo him y t.</p>\r\n<table class=\"picture\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"pic\"><img class=\"cms-photo ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"ng Trn Quang Bo (th 3 t tri qua) - Gim c S gio dc v o to tnh Kin Giang cng cc s ngnh nhn nt cng b ngy chuyn i s.\" src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/zshvwyvobvhvim/2023_12_25/cds2-2787.jpg\" alt=\"ng Trn Quang Bo (th 3 t tri qua) - Gim c S gio dc v o to tnh Kin Giang cng cc s ngnh nhn nt cng b ngy chuyn i s.\" width=\"840\" height=\"562\" data-height=\"723\" data-image-id=\"947632\" data-src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/zshvwyvobvhvim/2023_12_25/cds2-2787.jpg\" data-width=\"1080\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"caption\">\r\n<p>ng Trn Quang Bo (th 3 t tri qua) - Gim c S gio dc v o to tnh Kin Giang cng cc s ngnh nhn nt cng b ngy chuyn i s.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Cn theo S Gio dc v o to Kin Giang, thc hin chuyn i s gip ngnh i mi mnh m phng thc t chc gio dc. a vic dy v hc trn mi trng s tr thnh hot ng gio dc thit yu i vi mi nh gio, mi ngi hc nh: Trin khai, s dng hiu qu cc phn mm, thit b h tr son ging, tng tc vi hc sinh. Ngnh  i mi phng thc qun l, iu hnh da trn cng ngh v d liu nh: Trin khai, s dng hiu qu phn mm qun l trng hc, k ton, th vin, tuyn sinh u cp, kim nh cht lng gio dc, ph cp gio dc, xa m ch, c s d liu ngnh, vn phng in t, trung tm iu hnh gio dc thng minh, lp hc thng minh.</p>\r\n<p>Gim c S Gio dc v o to tnh Kin Giang, ng Trn Quang Bo cho bit:  thc hin hiu qu chuyn i s, ngnh ch trng pht trin h sinh thi chuyn i s hot ng dy, hc, kim tra, nh gi v nghin cu khoa hc; trin khai ng b h thng thng tin qun l gio dc, o to v c s d liu ngnh. Ngnh y mnh tuyn truyn, ph bin nng cao nhn thc; o to, bi dng nng lc s cho i ng nh gio, cn b qun l gio dc, nhn vin v ngi hc; nng cao Ch s pht trin ngun nhn lc.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ads_middle\"></div>\r\n<table class=\"picture\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"pic\"><img class=\"cms-photo ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"Gim c S Gio dc v o to tnh Kin Giang, ng Trn Quang Bo pht biu ti hi ngh.\" src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/xpiulqmc/2023_12_25/z5009225727920-71c3e097da55b91d1564e3d8939c4125-1-2903.jpg\" alt=\"Gim c S Gio dc v o to tnh Kin Giang, ng Trn Quang Bo pht biu ti hi ngh.\" width=\"840\" height=\"560\" data-height=\"1365\" data-image-id=\"947744\" data-src=\"https://photo-cms-baophapluat.epicdn.me/w840/Uploaded/2023/xpiulqmc/2023_12_25/z5009225727920-71c3e097da55b91d1564e3d8939c4125-1-2903.jpg\" data-width=\"2047\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"caption\">\r\n<p>Gim c S Gio dc v o to tnh Kin Giang, ng Trn Quang Bo pht biu ti hi ngh.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Theo ng Bo, trong qu trnh thc hin, ngnh vn gp mt s kh khn nh: Nhn thc v nng lc, trnh  cng ngh thng tin ca mt s cng chc, vin chc cn hn ch; mt s cng chc, vin chc cha khai thc hiu qu cc cng c phc v chuyn i s; kinh ph mua sm trang thit b cn hn hp. Bn cnh , vic trin khai cng tc chuyn i s  cc trng cha ng b, cha kt ni lin thng ht c s d liu t c s gio dc vi cc c quan qun l phng Gio dc v o to, S Gio dc v o to. Do , nh hng n khai thc, bo co, thng k, d bo ca ngnh.</p>\r\n<p>V mt s nhim v, gii php thc hin chuyn i s ca ngnh, Gim c S Gio dc v o to Kin Giang cho hay: Thi gian ti, Ngnh tip tc tn dng tin b khoa hc cng ngh  thc y i mi sng to trong dy v hc; xy dng nn gio dc m thch ng trn nn tng s. Ch ng c th ha chi tit hn na v phn cng nhim v ca tng cp trong ngnh  thc hin cc hng mc, nhim v cng ngh thng tin v an ton thng tin; xy dng b tiu ch nh gi thc hin chuyn i s trong ngnh; t chc vic nh gi thc hin chuyn i s hng nm ti cc n v.</p>\r\n<p>Ngoi ra, Ngnh tng cng bi dng nng cao k nng v cng ngh thng tin cho cn b qun l, gio vin, hc sinh. V u tin tp hun, bi dng qua mng hoc kt hp, tp hun qua mng. Ni dung bi dng gn lin vi nhu cu thc tin v ng dng cng ngh thng tin ca ngnh.</p>\r\n<div class=\"ads_middle\"></div>\r\n<p>Cha dng li  , S Gio dc v o to tnh Kin Giang cn ban hnh hng dn xy dng cc tiu ch, quy nh, quy trnh chuyn mn khi s dng cc phn mm. Thng qua   chuyn cc quy trnh cng vic hin hnh sang thc hin trn mi trng mng, s dng cc h s in t thay cho h s giy ti cc c s gio dc. To c s php l cho nh trng trin khai thun li thc hin chuyn i s v bo m tnh hiu qu.</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 17, '2024-01-05 01:15:24', 674, '', '2024-01-06 05:56:01', 674, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2024-01-05 01:15:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intr