(27, 99, 'Thiu n din o p, xung ph chp nh tt', 'thi-u-n-di-n-ao-d-p-xu-ng-ph-ch-p-nh-t-t', '<p><em><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/image/2023/01/23/kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%203%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Nha%CC%83.jpg\" alt=\"kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%203%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Nha%CC%83\" /></em></p>\r\n', '\r\n<div class=\"newscontent\">\r\n<h2 class=\"title-italic\">(KGO) - Tt n, nhiu bn n din nhng chic o p, tht tha, xung ph to dng chp nh  ghi li nhng khonh khc ng nh trong nhng ngy xun Qu Mo 2023.</h2>\r\n<div class=\"newscontent\">\r\n<p>Tt QuMo nm 2023, ti TP. Rch Gi (Kin Giang), cc tuyn ng xung quanh Trung tm Thng mi Rch Gi,khu  th Ph Cng,khu  th mi ln bin Ty Bc TP. Rch Gi l nhng a im c nhiubn n nto dng chp nh. Nhng ni ny c trang tr nhiu hoa rc r sc mu, tiu cnh p, l....</p>\r\n<p>Cc c gi Kin Giang xinh xn, du dng bn nhng b trang phc p i du xun,to dng chp nh,t thm thm cho ph phng lc xun sang.</p>\r\n<p><em><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/image/2023/01/23/kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%201%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Nha%CC%83.jpg\" alt=\"kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%201%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Nha%CC%83\" /></em></p>\r\n<p><em>Bn Phm Tin Dc, ng TP. Rch Gidin o di tht tha, ghi li khonh khc p ti Trung tm Thng mi Rch Gi.nh: THANH NH.</em></p>\r\n<p><em><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/image/2023/01/23/kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%204%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Thanh.jpg\" alt=\"kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%204%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Thanh\" /></em></p>\r\n<p><em>Bn Tng Kiu Phng, huyn Tn Hipni bt trong chic o di  kiu dng truyn thng. nh: THANH THANH.</em></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><em><img src=\"https://cdn.baokiengiang.vn/uploads/image/2023/01/23/kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%2015%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n