an><\\/button><\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vidverto__contextmenu\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vidverto__contextmenu-item\\\">Copy video url<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vidverto__contextmenu-item\\\">Play \\/ Pause<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vidverto__contextmenu-item\\\">Mute \\/ Unmute<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vidverto__contextmenu-item\\\">Report a problem<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vidverto__contextmenu-item\\\">Language<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vidverto__contextmenu-item\\\">Share<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vidverto__contextmenu-item\\\">Vidverto Player<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"vidverto__keyboard-hint-container\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"aries_uiElements\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"aries_controlIcon aries_closeControl\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"aries_controlIcon aries_volumeControl aries_mutedSpeaker aries_hidden\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"aries_caption aries_hcenter\\\">QU\\u1ea2NG C\\u00c1O<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n17 gi\\u1edd, khi \\u0111\\u1ebfn n\\u00fat giao \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng \\u0110\\u1ed3ng V\\u0103n C\\u1ed1ng - Mai Ch\\u00ed Th\\u1ecd (P.An Ph\\u00fa), th\\u00ec th\\u1ea5y c\\u00f3 3 \\u0111\\u1ee9a tr\\u1ebb (2 b\\u00e9 g\\u00e1i v\\u00e0 1 b\\u00e9 trai) \\u0111ang \\u0111\\u1ee9ng xin \\u0103n. Khi th\\u1ea5y t\\u1ed5 c\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c, 1 b\\u00e9 g\\u00e1i ch\\u1ea1y, 2 b\\u00e9 c\\u00f2n l\\u1ea1i ng\\u1ed3i kh\\u00f3c. T\\u1ed5 c\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0a c\\u00e1c em v\\u1ec1 P.An Ph\\u00fa \\u0111\\u1ec3 x\\u00e1c minh v\\u00e0 l\\u00e0m c\\u00e1c th\\u1ee7 t\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0a c\\u00e1c em v\\u1ec1 Trung t\\u00e2m h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i TP.HCM.\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<figure class=\\\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\\\">\\r\\n<figcaption class=\\\"PhotoCMS_Caption\\\">\\r\\n<p data-placeholder=\\\"Nh\\u1eadp ch\\u00fa th\\u00edch \\u1ea3nh\\\">3 \\u0111\\u1ee9a tr\\u1ebb xin \\u0103n t\\u1ea1i n\\u00fat giao th\\u00f4ng \\u0110\\u1ed3ng V\\u0103n C\\u1ed1ng - Mai Ch\\u00ed Th\\u1ecd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u01b0a v\\u1ec1 x\\u00e1c minh, sau \\u0111\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u01b0a v\\u00e0o Trung t\\u00e2m h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i TP.HCM<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/figcaption>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"PhotoCMS_Author\\\">\\r\\n<p data-placeholder=\\\"Nh\\u1eadp t\\u00e1c gi\\u1ea3\\\">TR\\u1eccNG NGH\\u0128A<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/figure>\\r\\n<p>Qua \\u0111\\u00f3, bi\\u1ebft 3 b\\u00e9 l\\u00e0 ch\\u1ecb em ru\\u1ed9t c\\u1ee7a nhau, b\\u00e9 g\\u00e1i l\\u1edbn 10 tu\\u1ed5i, b\\u00e9 trai 7 tu\\u1ed5i, b\\u00e9 g\\u00e1i nh\\u1ecf nh\\u1ea5t 2 tu\\u1ed5i. B\\u00e9 g\\u00e1i 10 tu\\u1ed5i t\\u00ean San, n\\u00f3i ti\\u1ebfng Vi\\u1ec7t kh\\u00f4ng r\\u00e0nh, cho hay 3 ch\\u1ecb em \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u1ee9ng xin \\u0103n t\\u1ea1i n\\u00fat giao th\\u00f4ng tr\\u00ean t\\u1eeb s\\u00e1ng, \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng cho 200.000 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng v\\u00e0 cho \\u0111\\u1ebfn th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ed5 c\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u01b0a v\\u1ec1 ph\\u01b0\\u1eddng th\\u00ec v\\u1eabn ch\\u01b0a \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0103n u\\u1ed1ng g\\u00ec.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\\"M\\u1ed7i ng\\u00e0y t\\u1ee5i con ph\\u1ea3i xin \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c 500.000 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng, n\\u1ebfu kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u1ee7 s\\u1ebd kh\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c cho \\u0103n v\\u00e0 s\\u1ebd b\\u1ecb cha \\u0111\\u00e1nh. Con \\u0111\\u1ee9ng \\u1edf \\u0111\\u00f3 xin, l\\u00e2u l\\u00e2u, cha con l\\u1ea1i l\\u1ea5y ti\\u1ec1n r\\u1ed3i \\u0111i, m\\u1ea5y con \\u0111\\u1ee9ng \\u0111\\u00f3 ti\\u1ebfp, n\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u1ee7 ti\\u1ec1n th\\u00ec th\\u00f4i\\\", b\\u00e9 g\\u00e1i n\\u00f3i v\\u00e0 cho hay kh\\u00f4ng bi\\u1ebft nh\\u00e0 \\u1edf \\u0111\\u00e2u, nh\\u01b0ng n\\u1ebfu t\\u1ef1 t\\u00ecm \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng v\\u1ec1 s\\u1ebd ra.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Sau khi x\\u00e1c minh l\\u00e0m c\\u00e1c th\\u1ee7 t\\u1ee5c b\\u00e0n giao cho P.An Ph\\u00fa \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0a c\\u00e1c b\\u00e9 v\\u1ec1 Trung t\\u00e2m h\\u1ed7 tr\\u1ee3 x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i TP.HCM, t\\u1ed5 c\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c TP.Th\\u1ee7 \\u0110\\u1ee9c ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c di chuy\\u1ec3n, tu\\u1ea7n tra c\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ecba b\\u00e0n kh\\u00e1c.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\\\" data-eid=\\\"\\\" data-embed-code=\\\"\\\" data-embed-json=\\\"\\\" data-id=\\\"0343456e-79de-4e3f-b1fb-4c24625c69b3\\\" data-oa=\\\"thanhnien\\\" data-style=\\\"align-center\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p>Kho\\u1ea3ng 19 gi\\u1edd, t\\u1ed5 c\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c ph\\u00e1t hi\\u1ec7n 2 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi g\\u1ed3m 1 c\\u1ee5 \\u00f4ng v\\u00e0 1 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u00e0n \\u00f4ng c\\u1edfi tr\\u1ea7n l\\u1ed9 r\\u00f5 c\\u00e1c v\\u1ebft b\\u1ecfng, \\u0111ang ng\\u1ed3i d\\u01b0\\u1edbi tr\\u1ee5 \\u0111\\u00e8n giao th\\u00f4ng, \\u0111o\\u1ea1n T\\u00f4 Ng\\u1ecdc V\\u00e2n - Ph\\u1ea1m V\\u0103n \\u0110\\u1ed3ng (P.Linh T\\u00e2y) v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng cho ti\\u1ec1n. T\\u1ed5 c\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0a 2 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi n\\u00e0y v\\u1ec1 tr\\u1ee5 s\\u1edf c\\u00f4ng an ph\\u01b0\\u1eddng l\\u00e0m c\\u00e1c th\\u1ee7 t\\u1ee5c x\\u00e1c minh.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"dable_placeholder\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"13\",\"created\":\"2024-01-05 01:10:14\",\"created_by\":\"674\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-01-05 01:10:14\",\"modified_by\":null,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2024-01-05 01:10:14\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":1,\"ordering\":null,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":null,\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"note\":\"\"}', 0),
(29, 15, 1, '', '2024-01-05 01:10:41', 674, 11565, '56cda7150e184e3d660aec4ae339ab6b1324aa42', '{\"id\":15,\"asset_id\":87,\"title\":\"\\u0110\\u1ed9i tuy\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam h\\u1ed9i qu\\u00e2n v\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng s\\u1ef1 v\\u1eafng m\\u1eb7t \\u0111\\u00e1ng ti\\u1ebfc\",\"alias\":\"d-i-tuy-n-vi-t-nam-h-i-quan-va-nh-ng-s-v-ng-m-t-dang-ti-c\",\"introtext\":\"<h2 class=\\\"detail-sapo fs-17 font-bitter fw-600 text-gray-44 mb-20\\\">(CLO) HLV Philippe Troussier v\\u1eeba c\\u00f4ng b\\u1ed1 danh s\\u00e1ch 34 tuy\\u1ec3n th\\u1ee7 Vi\\u1ec7t Nam chu\\u1ea9n b\\u1ecb cho v\\u00f2ng chung k\\u1ebft Asian Cup 2023, trong \\u0111\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u00f3ng vai tr\\u00f2 ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ea1o v\\u1eabn l\\u00e0 s\\u1ed1 c\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 v\\u1eeba chinh chi\\u1ebfn \\u1edf v\\u00f2ng lo\\u1ea1i th\\u1ee9 2 World Cup 2026 c\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u00e2y h\\u01a1n 1 th\\u00e1ng.<\\/h2>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"content-detail\\\">\\r\\n<p>Chi\\u1ec1u ng\\u00e0y 25\\/12, l\\u1ea7n \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean Li\\u00ean \\u0111o\\u00e0n b\\u00f3ng \\u0111\\u00e1 Vi\\u1ec7t Nam (VFF) c\\u00f4ng b\\u1ed1 danh s\\u00e1ch tri\\u1ec7u t\\u1eadp \\u0111\\u1ed9i tuy\\u1ec3n qu\\u1ed1c gia theo h\\u00ecnh th\\u1ee9c tr\\u1ef1c tuy\\u1ebfn tr\\u00ean c\\u00e1c n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng m\\u1ea1ng x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i YouTube, TikTok v\\u00e0 Facebook. 34 tuy\\u1ec3n th\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c g\\u1ecdi t\\u00ean, l\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng g\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1eb7t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c HLV Philippe Troussier v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ed9i ng\\u0169 tr\\u1ee3 l\\u00fd tuy\\u1ec3n ch\\u1ecdn, d\\u1ef1a tr\\u00ean danh s\\u00e1ch s\\u01a1 b\\u1ed9 50 c\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd l\\u00ean ban t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c Asian Cup 2023 c\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u00e2y 2 tu\\u1ea7n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<figure class=\\\"expNoEdit\\\"><a title=\\\"\\\"><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/congluan-cdn.congluan.vn\\/files\\/content\\/2023\\/12\\/26\\/doi-tuyen-viet-nam-hoi-quan-va-nhung-su-vang-mat-dang-tiec-103720927.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"doi tuyen viet nam hoi quan va nhung su vang mat dang tiec hinh 1\\\" width=\\\"1500\\\" height=\\\"1000\\\" data-img-mobile=\\\"undefined\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\r\\n<figcaption>\\r\\n<p>T\\u1ea5n T\\u00e0i kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 t\\u00ean trong danh s\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u1ed9i tuy\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam chu\\u1ea9n b\\u1ecb cho Asian Cup 2023<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/figcaption>\\r\\n<\\/figure>\\r\\n<p>V\\u1ec1 c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n, ph\\u1ea7n l\\u1edbn c\\u00e1c c\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 trong danh s\\u00e1ch n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1ec1u v\\u1eeba h\\u1ed9i qu\\u00e2n c\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u00e2y h\\u01a1n 1 th\\u00e1ng cho chi\\u1ebfn d\\u1ecbch v\\u00f2ng lo\\u1ea1i th\\u1ee9 2 World Cup 2026, g\\u1eb7p Philippines v\\u00e0 Iraq. 2 th\\u1ee7 th\\u00e0nh \\u0110\\u1eb7ng V\\u0103n L\\u00e2m v\\u00e0 Nguy\\u1ec5n \\u0110\\u00ecnh Tri\\u1ec7u ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c c\\u00f3 t\\u00ean, nh\\u01b0ng s\\u1ebd \\u0111\\u1ed1i m\\u1eb7t v\\u1edbi th\\u1eed th\\u00e1ch l\\u1edbn mang t\\u00ean Nguy\\u1ec5n Filip l\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ea7u l\\u00ean tuy\\u1ec3n sau khi nh\\u1eadp t\\u1ecbch th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng. H\\u00e0ng th\\u1ee7 v\\u1eabn l\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng c\\u00e1i t\\u00ean quen thu\\u1ed9c nh\\u01b0 Vi\\u1ec7t Anh, V\\u0103n Thanh, Thanh B\\u00ecnh, Tu\\u1ea5n T\\u00e0i, trong khi h\\u00e0ng c\\u00f4ng v\\u1eabn do Tu\\u1ea5n Anh, Tu\\u1ea5n H\\u1ea3i, V\\u0103n To\\u00e0n, Ti\\u1ebfn Linh\\u2026 g\\u1ed3ng g\\u00e1nh.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Tuy nhi\\u00ean, b\\u1ea3n danh s\\u00e1ch tri\\u1ec7u t\\u1eadp c\\u1ee7a HLV Philippe Troussier v\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u1ea1i kh\\u00f4ng \\u00edt ti\\u1ebfc nu\\u1ed1i cho ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi h\\u00e2m m\\u1ed9, b\\u1edfi s\\u1ef1 v\\u1eafng m\\u1eb7t c\\u1ee7a m\\u1ed9t v\\u00e0i c\\u00e1i t\\u00ean nh\\u01b0 Nguy\\u1ec5n V\\u0103n Quy\\u1ebft, \\u0110o\\u00e0n V\\u0103n H\\u1eadu, Nguy\\u1ec5n C\\u00f4ng Ph\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng hay \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 H\\u1ed3 T\\u1ea5n T\\u00e0i - m\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng h\\u1eadu v\\u1ec7 ph\\u1ea3i xu\\u1ea5t s\\u1eafc nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a b\\u00f3ng \\u0111\\u00e1 Vi\\u1ec7t Nam hi\\u1ec7n t\\u1ea1i.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>V\\u1ec1 ph\\u1ea7n V\\u0103n Quy\\u1ebft, th\\u1ee7 qu\\u00e2n c\\u1ee7a H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i FC v\\u1eabn \\u0111ang l\\u00e0 ch\\u00e2n s\\u00fat ghi nhi\\u1ec1u b\\u00e0n th\\u1eafng th\\u1ee9 2 trong l\\u1ecbch s\\u1eed \\u0111\\u1ed9i tuy\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam, c\\u00f2n \\u0111ang thi \\u0111\\u1ea5u. V\\u0103n Quy\\u1ebft ghi 16 b\\u00e0n sau 58 l\\u1ea7n ra s\\u00e2n, k\\u00e9m 2 b\\u00e0n so v\\u1edbi Ti\\u1ebfn Linh. L\\u1ea7n th\\u1ee9 2 li\\u00ean ti\\u1ebfp h\\u01b0\\u1edbng t\\u1edbi Asian Cup, \\u201cl\\u00e3o t\\u01b0\\u1edbng\\u201d sinh n\\u0103m 1991 kh\\u00f4ng g\\u00f3p m\\u1eb7t tr\\u00ean tuy\\u1ec3n, b\\u1edfi HLV Philippe Troussier mu\\u1ed1n t\\u1ea1o c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i cho nh\\u1eefng g\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1eb7t tr\\u1ebb h\\u01a1n \\u0111ang c\\u00f3 phong \\u0111\\u1ed9 cao nh\\u01b0 Ti\\u1ebfn Linh, \\u0110\\u00ecnh B\\u1eafc, Tu\\u1ea5n H\\u1ea3i hay V\\u0103n To\\u00e0n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Vi\\u1ec7c V\\u0103n H\\u1eadu l\\u1ee1 chuy\\u1ebfn xe l\\u00ean tuy\\u1ec3n c\\u0169ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 l\\u1ea1i nhi\\u1ec1u ti\\u1ebfc nu\\u1ed1i, ngay c\\u1ea3 v\\u1edbi ch\\u00ednh HLV Philippe Troussier. H\\u1eadu v\\u1ec7 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi Th\\u00e1i B\\u00ecnh l\\u00e0 nh\\u00e2n t\\u1ed1 quan tr\\u1ecdng v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ed9i tuy\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam, duy tr\\u00ec phong \\u0111\\u1ed9 xu\\u1ea5t s\\u1eafc \\u1edf m\\u00f9a gi\\u1ea3i tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc trong h\\u00e0nh tr\\u00ecnh c\\u00f9ng CLB C\\u00f4ng an H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i v\\u00f4 \\u0111\\u1ecbch V.League 2023. Tuy nhi\\u00ean, V\\u0103n H\\u1eadu l\\u1ea1i ph\\u1ea3i ngh\\u1ec9 thi \\u0111\\u1ea5u t\\u1eeb th\\u00e1ng 9 v\\u1eeba qua cho t\\u1edbi nay do v\\u1eabn \\u0111ang \\u0111i\\u1ec1u tr\\u1ecb ch\\u1ea5n th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng g\\u00f3t ch\\u00e2n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u1ede 2 l\\u1ea7n h\\u1ed9i qu\\u00e2n g\\u1ea7n nh\\u1ea5t, cho lo\\u1ea1t tr\\u1eadn giao h\\u1eefu d\\u1ecbp FIFA Days th\\u00e1ng 10 v\\u00e0 v\\u00f2ng lo\\u1ea1i th\\u1ee9 2 World Cup 2026 v\\u00e0o th\\u00e1ng 11, C\\u00f4ng Ph\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng \\u0111\\u1ec1u kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 t\\u00ean l\\u00ean tuy\\u1ec3n. Thay v\\u00ec tr\\u1edf l\\u1ea1i V.League t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i ra s\\u00e2n nh\\u01b0 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ed3ng \\u0111\\u1ed9i V\\u0103n To\\u00e0n, C\\u00f4ng Ph\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng l\\u1ea1i quy\\u1ebft t\\u00e2m g\\u1eafn b\\u00f3 v\\u1edbi Yokohama FC d\\u00f9 li\\u00ean t\\u1ee5c b\\u1ecb ng\\u00f3 l\\u01a1, th\\u1eadm ch\\u00ed c\\u00f2n kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 t\\u00ean trong danh s\\u00e1ch \\u0111\\u0103ng k\\u00fd thi \\u0111\\u1ea5u.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>T\\u00ednh t\\u1edbi nay, c\\u1ef1u ti\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u1ea1o c\\u1ee7a CLB Ho\\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai m\\u1edbi c\\u00f3 v\\u1ecfn v\\u1eb9n 2 ph\\u00fat kho\\u00e1c \\u00e1o \\u0111\\u1ed9i b\\u00f3ng Nh\\u1eadt B\\u1ea3n, trong khi HLV Philippe Troussier lu\\u00f4n nh\\u1eafc nh\\u1edf c\\u00e1c c\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 c\\u1ea7n n\\u1ed7 l\\u1ef1c \\u0111\\u1ec3 t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfn c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i ra s\\u00e2n thi \\u0111\\u1ea5u. Do \\u0111\\u00f3, vi\\u1ec7c C\\u00f4ng Ph\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng b\\u1ecb g\\u1ea1ch t\\u00ean trong danh s\\u00e1ch d\\u1ef1 Asian Cup 2023 th\\u1ef1c ra c\\u0169ng kh\\u00f4ng b\\u1ea5t ng\\u1edd.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"adv ads_id_35\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p>V\\u1edbi tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ee3p c\\u1ee7a T\\u1ea5n T\\u00e0i, m\\u1eb7c d\\u00f9 h\\u1eadu v\\u1ec7 CLB C\\u00f4ng an H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i duy tr\\u00ec phong \\u0111\\u1ed9 \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh, nh\\u01b0ng HLV Philippe Troussier l\\u1ea1i \\u01b0u ti\\u00ean nh\\u1eefng c\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 \\u0111a n\\u0103ng, c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 thi \\u0111\\u1ea5u \\u1edf nhi\\u1ec1u v\\u1ecb tr\\u00ed, qua \\u0111\\u00f3 gi\\u00fap qu\\u00e1 tr\\u00ecnh xoay tua ho\\u1eb7c thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i chi\\u1ebfn thu\\u1eadt tr\\u1edf n\\u00ean d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng v\\u00e0 nhanh ch\\u00f3ng. Ph\\u1ea1m Xu\\u00e2n M\\u1ea1nh hay c\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 tr\\u1ebb Tr\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Ti\\u1ebfn Anh hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ec1u c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u00e1 t\\u1ed1t b\\u00ean c\\u00e1nh ph\\u1ea3i. Ngo\\u00e0i ra, \\u0110\\u1ee9c Chi\\u1ebfn c\\u0169ng v\\u1eeba c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u00e1 h\\u1eadu v\\u1ec7 l\\u1eabn trung v\\u1ec7, hay k\\u1ec3 c\\u1ea3 ti\\u1ec1n v\\u1ec7 Tri\\u1ec7u Vi\\u1ec7t H\\u01b0ng c\\u0169ng t\\u1eebng \\u0111\\u00e1 h\\u1eadu v\\u1ec7 t\\u1ea1i CLB H\\u1ea3i Ph\\u00f2ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Theo k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch, \\u0111\\u1ed9i tuy\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam s\\u1ebd h\\u1ed9i qu\\u00e2n t\\u1eeb ng\\u00e0y 28\\/12 t\\u1ea1i H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i. T\\u1edbi ng\\u00e0y 5\\/1\\/2024, th\\u1ea7y tr\\u00f2 HLV Philippe Troussier s\\u1ebd l\\u00ean \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng sang Qatar t\\u1eadp hu\\u1ea5n v\\u00e0 t\\u1edbi ng\\u00e0y 9\\/1 th\\u00ec c\\u00f3 tr\\u1eadn giao h\\u1eefu v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ed9i tuy\\u1ec3n Kyrgyzstan.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>DANH S\\u00c1CH \\u0110\\u1ed8I TUY\\u1ec2N VI\\u1ec6T NAM<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Th\\u1ee7 m\\u00f4n (3):<\\/strong>\\u00a0Nguy\\u1ec5n Filip (C\\u00f4ng an H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i), Nguy\\u1ec5n \\u0110\\u00ecnh Tri\\u1ec7u (H\\u1ea3i Ph\\u00f2ng), \\u0110\\u1eb7ng V\\u0103n L\\u00e2m (B\\u00ecnh \\u0110\\u1ecbnh)<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>H\\u1eadu v\\u1ec7 (12):<\\/strong>\\u00a0V\\u00f5 Minh Tr\\u1ecdng, Qu\\u1ebf Ng\\u1ecdc H\\u1ea3i (B\\u00ecnh D\\u01b0\\u01a1ng), Gi\\u00e1p Tu\\u1ea5n D\\u01b0\\u01a1ng, H\\u1ed3 V\\u0103n C\\u01b0\\u1eddng, B\\u00f9i Ho\\u00e0ng Vi\\u1ec7t Anh, V\\u0169 V\\u0103n Thanh (C\\u00f4ng an H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i), \\u0110\\u1ed7 Duy M\\u1ea1nh, Nguy\\u1ec5n Th\\u00e0nh Chung (H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i), L\\u00ea Ng\\u1ecdc B\\u1ea3o, \\u0110\\u1ed7 Thanh Th\\u1ecbnh (B\\u00ecnh \\u0110\\u1ecbnh), Nguy\\u1ec5n Thanh B\\u00ecnh, Phan Tu\\u1ea5n T\\u00e0i (Th\\u1ec3 C\\u00f4ng Viettel)<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Ti\\u1ec1n v\\u1ec7 (13):<\\/strong>\\u00a0Ph\\u1ea1m Xu\\u00e2n M\\u1ea1nh, Nguy\\u1ec5n Hai Long, \\u0110\\u1ed7 H\\u00f9ng D\\u0169ng (H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i), Nguy\\u1ec5n Tu\\u1ea5n Anh (HAGL), Nguy\\u1ec5n Quang H\\u1ea3i, L\\u00ea Ph\\u1ea1m Th\\u00e0nh Long, Ho\\u00e0ng V\\u0103n To\\u1ea3n (C\\u00f4ng An H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i), Tri\\u1ec7u Vi\\u1ec7t H\\u01b0ng (H\\u1ea3i Ph\\u00f2ng), Nguy\\u1ec5n Ho\\u00e0ng \\u0110\\u1ee9c, Nguy\\u1ec5n \\u0110\\u1ee9c Chi\\u1ebfn, Tr\\u01b0\\u01a1ng Ti\\u1ebfn Anh, Khu\\u1ea5t V\\u0103n Khang (Th\\u1ec3 C\\u00f4ng Viettel), Nguy\\u1ec5n Th\\u00e1i S\\u01a1n (Thanh H\\u00f3a)<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Ti\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u1ea1o (6):<\\/strong>\\u00a0Nguy\\u1ec5n V\\u0103n To\\u00e0n (Nam \\u0110\\u1ecbnh), Nguy\\u1ec5n Ti\\u1ebfn Linh (B\\u00ecnh D\\u01b0\\u01a1ng), Ph\\u1ea1m Tu\\u1ea5n H\\u1ea3i, Nguy\\u1ec5n V\\u0103n T\\u00f9ng (H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i), Nguy\\u1ec5n Thanh Nh\\u00e0n (PVF-CAND), Nguy\\u1ec5n \\u0110\\u00ecnh B\\u1eafc (Qu\\u1ea3ng Nam)<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"13\",\"created\":\"2024-01-05 01:10:41\",\"created_by\":\"674\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-01-05 01:10:41\",\"modified_by\":null,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2024-01-05 01:10:41\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\