(31, 17, 1, '', '2024-01-05 01:11:18', 674, 7019, '82a5880c1fb064e64b54c8157fc52d7a800e92c5', '{\"id\":17,\"asset_id\":89,\"title\":\"C\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t nh\\u1ea5t tuy\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam b\\u00e1o tin bu\\u1ed3n cho HLV Troussier s\\u00e1t ng\\u00e0y h\\u1ed9i qu\\u00e2n\",\"alias\":\"c-u-th-d-c-bi-t-nh-t-tuy-n-vi-t-nam-bao-tin-bu-n-cho-hlv-troussier-sat-ngay-h-i-quan\",\"introtext\":\"<div class=\\\"detail__cnt-top\\\">\\r\\n<h3 class=\\\"text detail-sapo\\\" data-role=\\\"sapo\\\" data-type=\\\"sapo\\\">Ti\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u1ea1o Nguy\\u1ec5n Thanh Nh\\u00e0n cho bi\\u1ebft b\\u1ea3n th\\u00e2n d\\u00ednh ch\\u1ea5n th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v\\u00e0 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 s\\u1ebd r\\u00fat lui kh\\u1ecfi \\u0111\\u1ed9i tuy\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam.<\\/h3>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"detail-cmain\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"detail-content afcbc-body \\\" data-role=\\\"content\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"detail-cover\\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<p>H\\u00f4m 25\\/12, \\u0111\\u1ed9i tuy\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00f4ng b\\u1ed1 danh s\\u00e1ch 34 c\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ec3 h\\u01b0\\u1edbng \\u0111\\u1ebfn Asian Cup 2023.<\\/p>\\r\\n<figure class=\\\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\\\">\\r\\n<div><a class=\\\"detail-img-lightbox\\\" title=\\\"Thanh Nh\\u00e0n d\\u00ednh ch\\u1ea5n th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m l\\u00ean tuy\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam.\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/baogiaothong.mediacdn.vn\\/603483875699699712\\/2023\\/12\\/26\\/thanh-nhan-1703562583458849614624.jpg\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" data-fancybox=\\\"img-lightbox\\\"><img id=\\\"img_663952401959886848\\\" class=\\\"lightbox-content\\\" title=\\\"C\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t nh\\u1ea5t tuy\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam b\\u00e1o tin bu\\u1ed3n cho HLV Troussier s\\u00e1t ng\\u00e0y h\\u1ed9i qu\\u00e2n  - \\u1ea2nh 1.\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/baogiaothong.mediacdn.vn\\/603483875699699712\\/2023\\/12\\/26\\/thanh-nhan-1703562583458849614624.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"C\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t nh\\u1ea5t tuy\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam b\\u00e1o tin bu\\u1ed3n cho HLV Troussier s\\u00e1t ng\\u00e0y h\\u1ed9i qu\\u00e2n  - \\u1ea2nh 1.\\\" width=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"\\\" data-author=\\\"\\\" data-original=\\\"https:\\/\\/baogiaothong.mediacdn.vn\\/603483875699699712\\/2023\\/12\\/26\\/thanh-nhan-1703562583458849614624.jpg\\\" \\/><\\/a><\\/div>\\r\\n<figcaption class=\\\"PhotoCMS_Caption\\\">\\r\\n<p class=\\\"\\\" data-placeholder=\\\"Nh\\u1eadp ch\\u00fa th\\u00edch \\u1ea3nh\\\">Thanh Nh\\u00e0n d\\u00ednh ch\\u1ea5n th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m l\\u00ean tuy\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/figcaption>\\r\\n<\\/figure>\\r\\n<p>Trong l\\u1ea7n h\\u1ed9i qu\\u00e2n n\\u00e0y, b\\u00ean c\\u1ea1nh c\\u00e1c tr\\u1ee5 c\\u1ed9t, HLV Troussier ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c trao c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i cho d\\u00e0n c\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 tr\\u1ebb.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>M\\u1ed9t trong s\\u1ed1 nh\\u1eefng c\\u00e1i t\\u00ean \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nh\\u00e0 c\\u1ea7m qu\\u00e2n ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi Ph\\u00e1p trao c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i ch\\u00ednh l\\u00e0 ti\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u1ea1o Nguy\\u1ec5n Thanh Nh\\u00e0n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Nh\\u01b0ng \\u0111\\u00e1ng ti\\u1ebfc, ch\\u1ec9 sau \\u00edt gi\\u1edd \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c g\\u1ecdi l\\u00ean tuy\\u1ec3n, Thanh Nh\\u00e0n \\u0111\\u00e3 x\\u00e1c nh\\u1eadn b\\u1ea3n th\\u00e2n d\\u00ednh ch\\u1ea5n th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng v\\u00e0 kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng cao s\\u1ebd r\\u00fat lui.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u201cT\\u00f4i g\\u1eb7p ch\\u1ea5n th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng c\\u1ed5 ch\\u00e2n \\u1edf tr\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ea5u gi\\u1eefa PVF \\u2013 CAND v\\u1edbi Hu\\u1ebf t\\u1ea1i gi\\u1ea3i h\\u1ea1ng Nh\\u1ea5t qu\\u1ed1c gia.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>D\\u1ef1 ki\\u1ebfn ph\\u1ea3i m\\u1ea5t 2-3 tu\\u1ea7n m\\u1edbi c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 h\\u1ed3i ph\\u1ee5c n\\u00ean t\\u00f4i \\u0111\\u00e3 th\\u00f4ng b\\u00e1o cho c\\u00e2u l\\u1ea1c b\\u1ed9 ch\\u1ee7 qu\\u1ea3n v\\u00e0 ph\\u00eda \\u0111\\u1ed9i tuy\\u1ec3n v\\u1ec1 t\\u00ecnh h\\u00ecnh ch\\u1ea5n th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u00f3 ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u00e1n d\\u1ef1 ph\\u00f2ng\\u201d, Thanh Nh\\u00e0n chia s\\u1ebb.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Thanh Nh\\u00e0n l\\u00e0 c\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 duy nh\\u1ea5t \\u1edf gi\\u1ea3i h\\u1ea1ng Nh\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c HLV Troussier g\\u1ecdi l\\u00ean h\\u1ed9i qu\\u00e2n \\u0111\\u1ec3 h\\u01b0\\u1edbng \\u0111\\u1ebfn Asian Cup 2023.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>C\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 thu\\u1ed9c bi\\u00ean ch\\u1ebf PVF \\u2013 CAND \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u0111\\u00e1nh gi\\u00e1 r\\u1ea5t ti\\u1ec1m n\\u0103ng khi anh s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng d\\u1ee9t \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u1ea5n t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng, xoay x\\u1edf t\\u1ed1t.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Vi\\u1ec7c Thanh Nh\\u00e0n d\\u00ednh ch\\u1ea5n th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ngay tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc th\\u1eddi \\u0111i\\u1ec3m h\\u1ed9i qu\\u00e2n l\\u00e0 t\\u1ed5n th\\u1ea5t l\\u1edbn c\\u1ee7a tuy\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Nh\\u01b0ng may m\\u1eafn, trong tay HLV Troussier l\\u00fac n\\u00e0y \\u0111ang c\\u00f3 nh\\u1eefng c\\u00e1i t\\u00ean r\\u1ea5t ch\\u1ea5t l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng nh\\u01b0 Tu\\u1ea5n H\\u1ea3i, V\\u0103n To\\u00e0n hay Ti\\u1ebfn Linh.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u0110\\u00e1ng n\\u00f3i, nh\\u1eefng ng\\u00f4i sao n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1ec1u \\u0111ang d\\u1ea7n l\\u1ea5y l\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c phong \\u0111\\u1ed9 trong m\\u00e0u \\u00e1o CLB tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi l\\u00ean tuy\\u1ec3n.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Theo k\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch, ng\\u00e0y 31\\/12, tuy\\u1ec3n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam s\\u1ebd h\\u1ed9i qu\\u00e2n t\\u1ea1i Trung t\\u00e2m \\u0111\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o b\\u00f3ng \\u0111\\u00e1 tr\\u1ebb Vi\\u1ec7t Nam.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>T\\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2023, \\u0111o\\u00e0n qu\\u00e2n \\u00e1o \\u0111\\u1ecf l\\u1ea7n l\\u01b0\\u1ee3t \\u0111\\u1ee5ng \\u0111\\u1ed9 Nh\\u1eadt B\\u1ea3n (14\\/1\\/2024), Indonesia (19\\/1) v\\u00e0 Iraq (24\\/1).<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"13\",\"created\":\"2024-01-05 01:11:18\",\"created_by\":\"674\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-01-05 01:11:18\",\"modified_by\":null,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2024-01-05 01:11:18\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":1,\"ordering\":null,\"metakey\":\"\",\"metades