(64, 5, 1, '', '2024-01-05 01:23:27', 674, 4561, '4a0e121cfd0023ca26053fc0584a417a45b93a8b', '{\"id\":5,\"asset_id\":\"77\",\"title\":\"G\\u1ea7n 900 v\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng vi\\u00ean TP. H\\u00e0 Ti\\u00ean tham gia h\\u1ed9i kh\\u1ecfe Ph\\u00f9 \\u0110\\u1ed5ng\",\"alias\":\"g-n-900-v-n-d-ng-vien-tp-ha-tien-tham-gia-h-i-kh-e-phu-d-ng\",\"introtext\":\"<h2 class=\\\"title-italic\\\">(KGO) - S\\u00e1ng 23-12, TP. H\\u00e0 Ti\\u00ean (Ki\\u00ean Giang) t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c khai m\\u1ea1c h\\u1ed9i kh\\u1ecfe Ph\\u00f9 \\u0110\\u1ed5ng l\\u1ea7n th\\u1ee9 XX, n\\u0103m h\\u1ecdc 2023-2024.<\\/h2>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"newscontent\\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ANM_ABC.vn_Article_mid\\\">\\u00a0\",\"fulltext\":\"<\\/div>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.baokiengiang.vn\\/uploads\\/images\\/2023\\/12\\/23\\/113619kgo_20231223_PHU%20DONG%201.webp\\\" alt=\\\"113619kgo_20231223_PHU DONG 1\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>Ti\\u1ebft m\\u1ee5c bi\\u1ec3u di\\u1ec5n v\\u00f5 thu\\u1eadt ch\\u00e0o m\\u1eebng h\\u1ed9i kh\\u1ecfe Ph\\u00f9 \\u0110\\u1ed5ng\\u00a0<\\/em><em>TP. H\\u00e0 Ti\\u00ean\\u00a0<\\/em><em>l\\u1ea7n th\\u1ee9 XX,\\u00a0<\\/em><em>n\\u0103m h\\u1ecdc 2023-2024.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>H\\u1ed9i kh\\u1ecfe Ph\\u00f9 \\u0110\\u1ed5ng\\u00a0TP. H\\u00e0 Ti\\u00ean n\\u0103m h\\u1ecdc 2023-2024\\u00a0c\\u00f3 900 v\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng vi\\u00ean tham gia tranh t\\u00e0i\\u00a09 m\\u00f4n thi \\u0111\\u1ea5u g\\u1ed3m\\u00a0b\\u00f3ng \\u0111\\u00e1 nam, b\\u00f3ng chuy\\u1ec1n, c\\u1edd vua, c\\u1ea7u l\\u00f4ng, \\u0111\\u00e1 c\\u1ea7u, \\u0111i\\u1ec1n kinh, b\\u01a1i, k\\u00e9o co v\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u1ea9y g\\u1eady.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.baokiengiang.vn\\/uploads\\/images\\/2023\\/12\\/23\\/113913kgo_20231223_PHU%20DONG%202.webp\\\" alt=\\\"113913kgo_20231223_PHU DONG 2\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>C\\u00e1c \\u0111\\u1ed9i tranh t\\u00e0i n\\u1ed9i dung\\u00a0<\\/em><em>b\\u00e1n k\\u1ebft\\u00a0<\\/em><em>k\\u00e9o co nam.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng ph\\u00f2ng Gi\\u00e1o d\\u1ee5c v\\u00e0 \\u0110\\u00e0o t\\u1ea1o TP. H\\u00e0 Ti\\u00ean Nguy\\u1ec5n V\\u0103n Ba cho bi\\u1ebft h\\u1ed9i kh\\u1ecfe Ph\\u00f9 \\u0110\\u1ed5ng l\\u00e0 ng\\u00e0y h\\u1ed9i l\\u1edbn c\\u1ee7a tu\\u1ed5i tr\\u1ebb h\\u1ecdc \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng; l\\u00e0 d\\u1ecbp \\u0111\\u1ec3 ng\\u00e0nh gi\\u00e1o d\\u1ee5c th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 \\u0111\\u1ea9y m\\u1ea1nh phong tr\\u00e0o r\\u00e8n luy\\u1ec7n v\\u00e0 thi \\u0111\\u1ea5u c\\u00e1c m\\u00f4n th\\u1ec3 thao. Th\\u00f4ng qua h\\u1ed9i kh\\u1ecfe Ph\\u00f9 \\u0110\\u1ed5ng, th\\u00e0nh ph\\u1ed1 tuy\\u1ec3n ch\\u1ecdn v\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng vi\\u00ean\\u00a0c\\u00f3 th\\u00e0nh t\\u00edch cao \\u0111\\u1ec3\\u00a0ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c b\\u1ed3i d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng, t\\u1eadp luy\\u1ec7n n\\u00e2ng cao th\\u00e0nh t\\u00edch tham gia h\\u1ed9i kh\\u1ecfe Ph\\u00f9 \\u0110\\u1ed5ng c\\u1ea5p t\\u1ec9nh.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Sau l\\u1ec5 khai m\\u1ea1c, c\\u00e1c v\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng vi\\u00ean thi \\u0111\\u1ea5u\\u00a0b\\u00e1n k\\u1ebft v\\u00e0 chung k\\u1ebft c\\u00e1c n\\u1ed9i dung b\\u00f3ng \\u0111\\u00e1, b\\u00f3ng chuy\\u1ec1n v\\u00e0 k\\u00e9o co.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Tin v\\u00e0 \\u1ea3nh:\\u00a0<strong>DANH TH\\u00c0NH<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2024-01-05 01:06:02\",\"created_by\":\"674\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-01-05 01:23:27\",\"modified_by\":\"674\",\"checked_out\":\"674\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-01-05 01:23:23\",\"publish_up\":\"2024-01-05 01:06:02\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"ur