(191, 27, 1, '', '2024-01-07 07:10:03', 674, 8018, 'bfc6ee50377a4453d873c245e701a608446a06a2', '{\"id\":27,\"asset_id\":\"99\",\"title\":\"Thi\\u1ebfu n\\u1eef di\\u1ec7n \\u00e1o \\u0111\\u1eb9p, xu\\u1ed1ng ph\\u1ed1 ch\\u1ee5p \\u1ea3nh t\\u1ebft\",\"alias\":\"thi-u-n-di-n-ao-d-p-xu-ng-ph-ch-p-nh-t-t\",\"introtext\":\"<p><img src=\\\"images\\/kgo20230122_A\\u0309NH 1 - thie\\u0302\\u0301u nu\\u031b\\u0303 du xua\\u0302n - Nha\\u0303.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><img src=\\\"images\\/images2430419_12A.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<h2 class=\\\"title-italic\\\">(KGO) - T\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ebfn, nhi\\u1ec1u b\\u1ea1n n\\u1eef di\\u1ec7n nh\\u1eefng chi\\u1ebfc \\u00e1o \\u0111\\u1eb9p, th\\u01b0\\u1edbt tha, xu\\u1ed1ng ph\\u1ed1 t\\u1ea1o d\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ee5p \\u1ea3nh \\u0111\\u1ec3 ghi l\\u1ea1i nh\\u1eefng kho\\u1ea3nh kh\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u00e1ng nh\\u1edb trong nh\\u1eefng ng\\u00e0y xu\\u00e2n Qu\\u00fd M\\u00e3o 2023.<\\/h2>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"newscontent\\\">\\r\\n<p>T\\u1ebft Qu\\u00fd\\u00a0M\\u00e3o n\\u0103m 2023, t\\u1ea1i TP. R\\u1ea1ch Gi\\u00e1 (Ki\\u00ean Giang), c\\u00e1c tuy\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1eddng xung quanh Trung t\\u00e2m Th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i R\\u1ea1ch Gi\\u00e1,\\u00a0khu \\u0111\\u00f4 th\\u1ecb Ph\\u00fa C\\u01b0\\u1eddng,\\u00a0khu \\u0111\\u00f4 th\\u1ecb m\\u1edbi l\\u1ea5n bi\\u1ec3n T\\u00e2y B\\u1eafc TP. R\\u1ea1ch Gi\\u00e1\\u2026 l\\u00e0 nh\\u1eefng \\u0111\\u1ecba \\u0111i\\u1ec3m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c nhi\\u1ec1u\\u00a0b\\u1ea1n n\\u1eef \\u0111\\u1ebfn\\u00a0t\\u1ea1o d\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ee5p \\u1ea3nh. Nh\\u1eefng n\\u01a1i n\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c trang tr\\u00ed nhi\\u1ec1u hoa r\\u1ef1c r\\u1ee1 s\\u1eafc m\\u00e0u, ti\\u1ec3u c\\u1ea3nh \\u0111\\u1eb9p, l\\u1ea1....<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>C\\u00e1c c\\u00f4 g\\u00e1i Ki\\u00ean Giang xinh x\\u1eafn, d\\u1ecbu d\\u00e0ng b\\u00ean nh\\u1eefng b\\u1ed9 trang ph\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u1eb9p \\u0111i du xu\\u00e2n,\\u00a0t\\u1ea1o d\\u00e1ng ch\\u1ee5p \\u1ea3nh,\\u00a0t\\u00f4 th\\u1eafm th\\u00eam cho ph\\u1ed1 ph\\u01b0\\u1eddng l\\u00fac xu\\u00e2n sang.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>B\\u1ea1n Ph\\u1ea1m Ti\\u1ebfn D\\u01b0\\u1ee3c, ng\\u1ee5 TP. R\\u1ea1ch Gi\\u00e1\\u00a0di\\u1ec7n \\u00e1o d\\u00e0i th\\u01b0\\u1edbt tha, ghi l\\u1ea1i kho\\u1ea3nh kh\\u1eafc \\u0111\\u1eb9p t\\u1ea1i Trung t\\u00e2m Th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i R\\u1ea1ch Gi\\u00e1.\\u00a0\\u1ea2nh: THANH NH\\u00c3.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.baokiengiang.vn\\/uploads\\/image\\/2023\\/01\\/23\\/kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%203%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Nha%CC%83.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%203%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Nha%CC%83\\\" \\/><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>B\\u1ea1n Cao Th\\u1ecb Quy\\u1ec1n Tr\\u00e2n, ng\\u1ee5 huy\\u1ec7n An Bi\\u00ean to\\u00e1t l\\u00ean v\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1eb9p d\\u1ecbu d\\u00e0ng\\u00a0khi di\\u1ec7n \\u00e1o d\\u00e0i \\u0111\\u1ecf ch\\u1ee5p \\u1ea3nh\\u00a0t\\u1ea1i m\\u1ed9t qu\\u1ea7y h\\u00e0ng trang tr\\u00ed t\\u1ebft thu\\u1ed9c\\u00a0Trung t\\u00e2m Th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng m\\u1ea1i R\\u1ea1ch Gi\\u00e1. \\u1ea2nh: THANH NH\\u00c3.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.baokiengiang.vn\\/uploads\\/image\\/2023\\/01\\/23\\/kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%204%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Thanh.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%204%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Thanh\\\" \\/><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>B\\u1ea1n T\\u0103ng Ki\\u1ec1u Ph\\u1ee5ng, huy\\u1ec7n T\\u00e2n Hi\\u1ec7p\\u00a0n\\u1ed5i b\\u1eadt trong chi\\u1ebfc \\u00e1o d\\u00e0i \\u0111\\u1ecf ki\\u1ec3u d\\u00e1ng truy\\u1ec1n th\\u1ed1ng. \\u1ea2nh: THANH THANH.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.baokiengiang.vn\\/uploads\\/image\\/2023\\/01\\/23\\/kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%206%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Thanh.JPG\\\" alt=\\\"kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%206%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Thanh\\\" \\/><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>Nh\\u1eefng ti\\u1ec3u c\\u1ea3nh d\\u00e2n d\\u00e3 g\\u1eafn v\\u1edbi t\\u1ebft t\\u1ea1i khu \\u0111\\u00f4 th\\u1ecb Ph\\u00fa C\\u01b0\\u1eddng, TP. R\\u1ea1ch Gi\\u00e1 c\\u0169ng thu h\\u00fat nhi\\u1ec1u ch\\u1ecb em \\u0111\\u1ebfn ch\\u1ee5p \\u1ea3nh \\u0111\\u00f3n t\\u1ebft. \\u1ea2nh: THANH THANH.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.baokiengiang.vn\\/uploads\\/image\\/2023\\/01\\/23\\/kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%208%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Thanh.JPG\\\" alt=\\\"kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%208%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Thanh\\\" \\/><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em>Ch\\u1ecb \\u0110\\u00e0o H\\u1ed3ng Ng\\u1ecdc, ng\\u1ee5 ph\\u01b0\\u1eddng V\\u0129nh Thanh, TP. R\\u1ea1ch Gi\\u00e1\\u00a0c\\u00f9ng ch\\u1ecb g\\u00e1i \\u0110\\u00e0o Th\\u1ecb Di\\u1ec5m H\\u01b0\\u01a1ng r\\u1ea1ng r\\u1ee1 v\\u1edbi\\u00a0b\\u1ed9 \\u00e1o d\\u00e0i d\\u1ea1o ch\\u01a1i ch\\u1ee3 hoa xu\\u00e2n.\\u00a0\\u1ea2nh: THANH THANH.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.baokiengiang.vn\\/uploads\\/image\\/2023\\/01\\/23\\/kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%2011%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Chuye%CC%82%CC%80n.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"kgo20230122_A%CC%89NH%2011%20-%20thie%CC%82%CC%81u%20nu%CC%9B%CC%83%20du%20xua%CC%82n%20-%20Chuye%CC%82%CC%80n\\\" \\/><\\/em><em>B\\u1ea1n Phan Ng\\u1ecdc S\\u1ef1, ng\\u1ee5 huy\\u1ec7n Gi\\u1ed3ng Ri\\u1ec1ng t\\u1ea1o d\\u00e1ng b\\u00ean ti\\u1ec3u c\\u1ea3nh n\\u1ed3i b\\u00e1nh t\\u00e9t ng\\u00e0y t\\u1ebft t\\u1ea1i khu \\u0111\\u00f4 th\\u1ecb Ph\\u00fa C\\u01b0\\u1eddng.\\u00a0<\\/em><em>\\u1ea2nh: \\u00daT CHUY\\u1ec0N.<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><em><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/cdn.baokiengiang.vn\\/uploads\\/image\\/20